1
00:03:05,102 --> 00:03:07,938
- [ Beeping, Chirping ]
- Lock onto him, R2.

2
00:03:08,021 --> 00:03:11,483
- [ Beeps ]
- Master, General Grievous's ship is directly ahead-

3
00:03:11,567 --> 00:03:13,819
the one crawling with vulture droids.

4
00:03:13,902 --> 00:03:16,446
Oh, I see it. Oh, this is going to be easy.

5
00:03:16,530 --> 00:03:19,741
[ Speaking Droid Language ]

6
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:26,665
Oddball, do you copy?
[ Man On Headset ]
Copy, Red Leader.

7
00:03:26,748 --> 00:03:29,042
Mark my position. Form your squad up behind me.

8
00:03:29,126 --> 00:03:31,044
We're on your tail, General Kenobi.

9
00:03:31,128 --> 00:03:33,088
Set S-foils in attack position.

10
00:03:46,977 --> 00:03:49,021
This is where the fun begins.

11
00:03:49,104 --> 00:03:51,148
Let them pass between us.

12
00:04:07,873 --> 00:04:11,835
- They're all over me. Get them off my-
- [ Static ]

13
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,837
I'm gonna go help them out.
[ Obi-Wan ]
No.

14
00:04:13,921 --> 00:04:16,673
No, they are doing their job so we can do ours.

15
00:04:19,343 --> 00:04:20,552
[ Screams ]

16
00:04:24,389 --> 00:04:27,643
[ Speaking Droid Language ]

17
00:04:30,604 --> 00:04:33,190
Missiles. Pull up.

18
00:04:34,608 --> 00:04:37,194
- They overshot us.
- They're coming around.

19
00:04:41,532 --> 00:04:44,368
- [ Beeping ]
- All right, R4.

20
00:04:44,451 --> 00:04:47,037
No, no, no, no- No, nothing too fancy.

21
00:04:50,249 --> 00:04:54,002
Surge all power units, R2.
Stand by reverse thrusters.

22
00:04:54,086 --> 00:04:56,547
- [ Engines Roaring ]
- [ Whistling ]

23
00:05:01,802 --> 00:05:05,389
- [ Chuckles ] We got 'em, R2.
- [ Beeps, Whistles ]

24
00:05:13,689 --> 00:05:15,732
Flying is for droids.

25
00:05:22,906 --> 00:05:26,743
- I'm hit. Anakin?
- I see them. Buzz droids.

26
00:05:26,827 --> 00:05:29,496
[ Cackling ]
[ R4 Whimpering ]

27
00:05:29,580 --> 00:05:33,041
- [ Squawking ]
- [ Chirping ]

28
00:05:34,334 --> 00:05:36,378
R4, be careful. You have a-

29
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:41,425
- [ Wailing ]
- Oh, dear.

30
00:05:43,552 --> 00:05:45,387
They're shutting down all the controls.

31
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:48,515
- Move to the right so I can get a clear shot at them.
- The mission.

32
00:05:48,599 --> 00:05:52,477
Get to the command ship. Get the chancellor.
I'm running out of tricks here.

33
00:05:55,355 --> 00:05:59,651
- [ Squealing ]
- Oh! In the name of-

34
00:06:01,945 --> 00:06:05,949
- Hold your fire! You're not helping here.
- I agree. Bad idea.

35
00:06:09,077 --> 00:06:10,787
[ Screams ]

36
00:06:12,331 --> 00:06:15,125
I can't see a thing. My cockpit's fogging.

37
00:06:18,378 --> 00:06:20,297
They're all over me. Anakin!

38
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:27,012
- Move to the right.
- Hold on, Anakin. You're gonna get us both killed.

39
00:06:29,515 --> 00:06:31,475
Get out of here.
There's nothing more you can do.

40
00:06:31,558 --> 00:06:33,769
I'm not leaving without you, Master.

41
00:06:37,314 --> 00:06:40,609
[ Buzzing ]

42
00:06:42,736 --> 00:06:45,572
- [ Beeping, Whistling ]
- Get him, R2.

43
00:06:45,656 --> 00:06:49,034
- [ Buzz Droid Squawks ]
- Watch out.

44
00:06:49,117 --> 00:06:51,328
[ Whistles ]

45
00:06:53,622 --> 00:06:55,958
R2, hit the buzz droid's center eye.

46
00:06:56,041 --> 00:06:57,835
[ Beeping ]

47
00:07:03,173 --> 00:07:05,509
- Yeah, you got him!
- Great, R2.

48
00:07:07,803 --> 00:07:09,721
The general's command ship is dead ahead.

49
00:07:09,805 --> 00:07:11,723
[ R2-D2 Squealing ]

50
00:07:11,807 --> 00:07:13,892
Well, have you noticed the shields are still up?

51
00:07:13,976 --> 00:07:16,019
Sorry, Master.

52
00:07:23,527 --> 00:07:25,654
Oh, I have a bad feeling about this.

53
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,629
There they are. Get them.

54
00:07:52,014 --> 00:07:56,143
- [ Beeping, Whistling ]
- R2, locate the chancellor.

55
00:07:56,226 --> 00:07:58,353
[ Chirps ]

56
00:07:58,437 --> 00:08:00,397
[ Groaning ]

57
00:08:02,941 --> 00:08:04,443
[ Whistles ]

58
00:08:04,526 --> 00:08:07,237
[ Obi-Wan ] The chancellor's signal
is coming from right there-

59
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:10,407
the observation platform
at the top of that spire.

60
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:12,451
I sense Count Dooku.

61
00:08:12,534 --> 00:08:15,829
I sense a trap.
Next move?

62
00:08:15,913 --> 00:08:19,499
- Spring the trap.
- [ Whistling ]

63
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:22,794
R2, go back.
I need you to stay with the ship.

64
00:08:22,878 --> 00:08:24,796
Here. Take this and wait for orders.

65
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:27,049
[ Beeping ]

66
00:08:30,093 --> 00:08:32,012
[ Growls ]

67
00:08:32,095 --> 00:08:34,723
[ Coughing ]

68
00:08:39,102 --> 00:08:42,606
What's the situation, Captain?

69
00:08:42,689 --> 00:08:46,652
Two Jedi have landed in the main hangar bay.
We're tracking them.

70
00:08:46,735 --> 00:08:51,031
Just as Count Dooku predicted.
[ Coughs ]

71
00:08:51,114 --> 00:08:54,368
[ Cackles ]

72
00:08:54,451 --> 00:08:56,286
[ Clattering ]
Destroyers.

73
00:09:04,461 --> 00:09:07,339
Drop your weapons. I said drop 'em.

74
00:09:07,422 --> 00:09:08,924
Roger.
Roger, roger.

75
00:09:09,007 --> 00:09:10,217
Roger, roger.

76
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,969
[ All Groaning ]

77
00:09:14,972 --> 00:09:16,640
[ Beeps ]

78
00:09:17,850 --> 00:09:19,768
Those are Jedi fighters all right.

79
00:09:19,852 --> 00:09:22,646
[ Beeps Softly ]

80
00:09:24,398 --> 00:09:26,400
Did you press the stop button?
No. Did you?

81
00:09:26,483 --> 00:09:29,778
- No.
- Well, there's more than one way out of here.

82
00:09:29,862 --> 00:09:31,697
[ Obi-Wan ]
We don't want to get out.

83
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:37,494
We want to get moving.
R2, activate elevator 31174.

84
00:09:37,578 --> 00:09:39,788
[ Obi-Wan On Comlink ]
Come in, R2.
What that?

85
00:09:39,872 --> 00:09:41,790
R2, do you copy?
[ Electronic Twittering ]

86
00:09:41,874 --> 00:09:43,792
R2, activate the elevator number...

87
00:09:43,876 --> 00:09:46,128
[ Muffled ]
31174.
[ Chirps Softly ]

88
00:09:46,211 --> 00:09:49,173
Get back to work. That nothin'.

89
00:09:49,256 --> 00:09:52,217
[ Obi-Wan, Muffled ]
Activate the elevator 31174.

90
00:09:52,301 --> 00:09:54,219
R2, we-

91
00:09:59,349 --> 00:10:01,935
[ Sighs ]
Always on the move.

92
00:10:02,019 --> 00:10:03,937
[ Obi-Wan, Muffled ]
R2, switch on the comlink.

93
00:10:04,021 --> 00:10:06,064
[ Obi-Wan On Comlink ]
R2, can you hear me?

94
00:10:06,148 --> 00:10:08,609
- R2?
- [ R2-D2 Beeps ]

95
00:10:08,692 --> 00:10:09,985
Whoa!

96
00:10:10,068 --> 00:10:12,196
[ Obi-Wan, Fading ]
R2! R2!

97
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,574
[ Beeping ]

98
00:10:15,657 --> 00:10:19,036
Stop. Stop. R2, we need to be going up.

99
00:10:21,455 --> 00:10:23,373
Hands up, Jedi.

100
00:10:23,457 --> 00:10:25,667
[ Obi-Wan On Comlink ]
R2, do you copy?

101
00:10:25,751 --> 00:10:29,755
R2, do you hear me?
R2, we need to be going up, not down.

102
00:10:30,923 --> 00:10:31,882
[ Groans ]

103
00:10:32,966 --> 00:10:34,510
[ Chirps ]

104
00:10:34,593 --> 00:10:37,596
- Hey, you!
- [ Beeping ]

105
00:10:40,766 --> 00:10:42,684
Now, that's better.

106
00:10:42,768 --> 00:10:47,064
- [ Beeps, Chirps ]
- You stupid little astro droid.

107
00:10:47,981 --> 00:10:50,275
- Uh-oh.
- [ Grunts ]

108
00:10:57,241 --> 00:10:59,159
Oh, it's you.

109
00:10:59,243 --> 00:11:01,203
[ Beeping ]
[ Groans ]

110
00:11:01,286 --> 00:11:03,121
My eyes! My eyes!

111
00:11:03,205 --> 00:11:05,666
What was that all about?
Well, R2 has been-

112
00:11:05,749 --> 00:11:08,710
Uh, no loose wire jokes.
Did I say anything?

113
00:11:08,794 --> 00:11:10,754
He's trying.
I didn't say anything.

114
00:11:10,838 --> 00:11:13,048
[ Beeping ]

115
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,971
[ Chirps ]

116
00:11:48,375 --> 00:11:50,294
Chancellor.
Are you all right?

117
00:11:50,377 --> 00:11:53,005
Count Dooku.

118
00:11:56,592 --> 00:12:00,470
This time we will do it together.
I was about to say that.

119
00:12:09,396 --> 00:12:12,608
Get help. You're no match for him.
He's a Sith lord.

120
00:12:12,691 --> 00:12:16,778
Chancellor Palpatine,
Sith lords are our speciality.

121
00:12:16,862 --> 00:12:19,781
Your swords, please.

122
00:12:19,865 --> 00:12:23,368
We don't want to make a mess of things
in front of the chancellor.

123
00:12:23,452 --> 00:12:25,704
You won't get away this time, Dooku.

124
00:12:36,632 --> 00:12:38,634
I've been looking forward to this.

125
00:12:38,717 --> 00:12:41,929
My powers have doubled
since the last time we met, Count.

126
00:12:42,012 --> 00:12:45,516
Good. Twice the pride, double the fall.

127
00:12:51,730 --> 00:12:53,023
[ Groans ]

128
00:13:05,577 --> 00:13:06,578
Get-

129
00:13:07,538 --> 00:13:09,414
[ Groans ]

130
00:13:23,095 --> 00:13:25,597
[ Grunts ]

131
00:13:31,812 --> 00:13:36,900
I sense great fear in you, Skywalker.

132
00:13:36,984 --> 00:13:40,654
You have hate. You have anger.

133
00:13:40,737 --> 00:13:42,698
But you don't use them.

134
00:13:57,421 --> 00:13:59,590
[ Groans ]

135
00:14:02,301 --> 00:14:06,096
Good, Anakin. Good.
[ Chuckling ]

136
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:08,223
Kill him.

137
00:14:09,683 --> 00:14:11,268
Kill him now.

138
00:14:16,899 --> 00:14:18,817
I shouldn't.

139
00:14:21,653 --> 00:14:22,779
Do it.

140
00:14:34,791 --> 00:14:37,711
You did well, Anakin.

141
00:14:37,794 --> 00:14:41,757
He was too dangerous to be kept alive.

142
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:44,259
Yes, but he was an unarmed prisoner.

143
00:14:44,343 --> 00:14:47,221
I shouldn't have done that.
It's not the Jedi way.

144
00:14:47,304 --> 00:14:52,476
It is only natural.
He cut off your arm, and you wanted revenge.

145
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:55,604
It wasn't the first time, Anakin.

146
00:14:55,687 --> 00:14:59,483
Remember what you told me
about your mother and the Sand People?

147
00:14:59,566 --> 00:15:02,152
[ Sand People Shouting, Faint ]

148
00:15:02,236 --> 00:15:05,864
Now we must leave
before more security droids arrive.

149
00:15:10,244 --> 00:15:13,247
Anakin, there's no time.

150
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:16,583
We must get off this ship before it's too late.

151
00:15:16,667 --> 00:15:20,712
- He seems to be all right.
- Leave him, or we'll never make it.

152
00:15:20,796 --> 00:15:23,507
His fate will be the same as ours.

153
00:15:27,928 --> 00:15:30,138
Prepare for attack!

154
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:34,351
All batteries, fire! Fire!

155
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,985
[ Screams ]

156
00:15:44,361 --> 00:15:46,321
Elevator's not working.

157
00:15:50,033 --> 00:15:52,703
R2, activate elevator 3224.

158
00:15:52,786 --> 00:15:55,581
[ Whistling, Beeping ]

159
00:16:01,753 --> 00:16:03,755
[ Groans ]

160
00:16:05,174 --> 00:16:07,593
[ Beeping ]

161
00:16:09,303 --> 00:16:11,305
[ Screaming ]

162
00:16:11,388 --> 00:16:14,641
- Reverse stabilizers.
- Reversing stabilizers.

163
00:16:14,725 --> 00:16:18,103
[ Beeping ]

164
00:16:28,113 --> 00:16:30,574
[ Squealing ]

165
00:16:33,911 --> 00:16:36,079
Magnetize! Magnetize!

166
00:16:38,457 --> 00:16:40,417
[ Squealing, Beeping ]

167
00:16:42,628 --> 00:16:45,964
Fire the emergency booster engines.

168
00:16:50,969 --> 00:16:52,888
We're leveling out, sir.

169
00:16:56,016 --> 00:16:58,477
Oh!

170
00:17:05,984 --> 00:17:08,529
[ Gasps ]

171
00:17:08,612 --> 00:17:10,822
[ Anakin ]
Easy. We're in a bit of a situation here.

172
00:17:10,906 --> 00:17:13,534
Did I miss something?
Hold on.

173
00:17:13,617 --> 00:17:15,827
- What is that?
- [ Anakin ] Uh, oops.

174
00:17:15,911 --> 00:17:17,913
R2. R2, shut down the elevator.

175
00:17:17,996 --> 00:17:19,957
Too late. Jump!

176
00:17:26,421 --> 00:17:27,464
[ Shouts ]

177
00:17:30,801 --> 00:17:31,969
[ All Groan ]

178
00:17:33,554 --> 00:17:37,224
[ Obi-Wan ] Let's see if we can find something
in the hangar bay that's still flyable.

179
00:17:37,307 --> 00:17:39,393
R2, get down here.
[ Groans ]

180
00:17:39,476 --> 00:17:41,770
[ Anakin On Comlink ]
R2, do you copy?

181
00:17:41,854 --> 00:17:45,607
[ Chirps, Whistles ]

182
00:17:45,691 --> 00:17:48,443
[ Wheezing, Coughing ]
General, we found the Jedi.

183
00:17:48,527 --> 00:17:52,990
They're in hallway 328.
Activate ray shields.

184
00:17:55,325 --> 00:17:57,244
Ray shields.

185
00:17:57,327 --> 00:17:59,246
Wait a minute. How did this happen?

186
00:17:59,329 --> 00:18:01,707
We're smarter than this.
Apparently not.

187
00:18:03,667 --> 00:18:06,879
I say patience.
Patience?

188
00:18:06,962 --> 00:18:10,257
Yes. R2 will be along in a few moments,

189
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:13,635
and then... he'll release the ray shields.

190
00:18:13,719 --> 00:18:15,637
[ Door Opens ]

191
00:18:15,721 --> 00:18:18,098
[ Squealing ]

192
00:18:18,182 --> 00:18:20,142
[ Sputters, Squeaks ]

193
00:18:20,225 --> 00:18:22,477
See? No problem.

194
00:18:22,561 --> 00:18:24,730
[ Speaking Droid Language ]

195
00:18:24,813 --> 00:18:26,732
Don't move.
[ Beeps ]

196
00:18:26,815 --> 00:18:28,692
Ow!

197
00:18:29,776 --> 00:18:32,654
Do you have a plan "B"?

198
00:18:38,327 --> 00:18:42,915
Ah, yes. The negotiator.

199
00:18:42,998 --> 00:18:47,252
General Kenobi. We've been waiting for you.

200
00:18:47,336 --> 00:18:49,505
[ Battle Droid ]
Excuse me.

201
00:18:49,588 --> 00:18:52,382
That wasn't much of a rescue.
You're welcome.

202
00:18:52,466 --> 00:18:54,927
And-
[ Coughs ]

203
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:57,804
Anakin Skywalker.

204
00:18:57,888 --> 00:19:03,644
I was expecting someone
with your reputation to be a little... older.

205
00:19:03,727 --> 00:19:05,646
[ Wheezes ]

206
00:19:05,729 --> 00:19:10,025
General Grievous.
You're shorter than I expected.

207
00:19:10,108 --> 00:19:14,655
[ Coughing ]
Jedi scum.

208
00:19:14,738 --> 00:19:17,533
We have a job to do, Anakin.
Try not to upset him.

209
00:19:17,616 --> 00:19:20,244
[ Beeps, Chirps ]

210
00:19:20,327 --> 00:19:22,246
[ Coughs ]

211
00:19:22,329 --> 00:19:27,000
Your lightsabers will make a fine addition
to my collection.

212
00:19:27,084 --> 00:19:30,796
Not this time.
And this time, you won't escape.

213
00:19:30,879 --> 00:19:33,131
R2.

214
00:19:33,215 --> 00:19:34,716
[ Squeals ]

215
00:19:36,885 --> 00:19:39,596
- Crush them!
- [ Alarm Blaring ]

216
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,765
Make them suffer!

217
00:19:45,769 --> 00:19:47,479
Come. Now!

218
00:19:47,563 --> 00:19:49,773
Stay at your stations!
Whoa!

219
00:19:51,733 --> 00:19:53,610
[ Rapid Beeping ]

220
00:19:56,405 --> 00:19:58,949
Get him! Get him!

221
00:20:01,326 --> 00:20:03,287
[ Battle Droid ]
Ow!

222
00:20:08,333 --> 00:20:10,627
[ Screams ]

223
00:20:17,259 --> 00:20:19,178
Run!

224
00:20:19,261 --> 00:20:22,639
- [ Groaning ]
- [ Sighs ]

225
00:20:22,723 --> 00:20:26,268
Don't bother with them.
Keep the ship in orbit.
Yes, sir.

226
00:20:26,351 --> 00:20:29,354
- [ Whimpering ]
- [ Shouts ]

227
00:20:29,438 --> 00:20:30,606
[ Squeaks, Beeps ]

228
00:20:37,279 --> 00:20:39,990
You lose, General Kenobi.

229
00:20:53,837 --> 00:20:56,006
[ Gasping ]

230
00:21:03,805 --> 00:21:05,891
Get out of here! Run!

231
00:21:16,610 --> 00:21:18,946
[ Cackles ]

232
00:21:19,029 --> 00:21:21,532
Time to abandon ship.

233
00:21:26,161 --> 00:21:28,664
[ Cackles, Coughs ]

234
00:21:28,747 --> 00:21:31,166
[ Alarm Beeping ]
All the escape pods
have been launched.

235
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:34,336
[ Obi-Wan ]
Grievous. Can you fly a cruiser like this?

236
00:21:34,419 --> 00:21:37,464
You mean, do I know how to land
what's left of this thing?
Well?

237
00:21:37,548 --> 00:21:41,134
Well, under the circumstances,
I'd say the ability to pilot this thing is irrelevant.

238
00:21:41,218 --> 00:21:42,427
Strap yourselves in.

239
00:21:44,179 --> 00:21:47,057
Open all hatches.
Extend all flaps and drag fins.

240
00:21:49,977 --> 00:21:52,020
[ Squeaking, Whistling ]

241
00:22:01,655 --> 00:22:05,951
- [ Beeps: "Uh-oh" ]
- We lost something.

242
00:22:06,034 --> 00:22:08,537
Not to worry. We are still flying half a ship.

243
00:22:11,790 --> 00:22:15,794
- [ Beeping ]
- Now we're really picking up speed.

244
00:22:24,428 --> 00:22:26,221
[ Obi-Wan ]
Eight plus 60.

245
00:22:26,305 --> 00:22:30,392
We're in the atmosphere.
Grab that. Keep us level.

246
00:22:35,397 --> 00:22:37,941
[ Chirping, Beeping ]

247
00:22:43,530 --> 00:22:46,658
- Steady.
- [ Beeping ]

248
00:22:46,742 --> 00:22:49,411
Easy, R2.

249
00:22:52,581 --> 00:22:56,293
5000. Fire ships on the left and the right.

250
00:22:56,376 --> 00:22:59,129
We'll take you in.
[ Obi-Wan ]
Copy that.

251
00:23:01,507 --> 00:23:05,302
- Landing strip, straight ahead.
- We're coming in too hot.

252
00:23:09,014 --> 00:23:11,683
[ Chirping, Whistling ]

253
00:23:14,311 --> 00:23:15,521
[ R2-D2 Squealing ]

254
00:23:17,898 --> 00:23:19,650
[ Squealing Continues ]

255
00:23:32,120 --> 00:23:35,999
- [ R2-D2 Chirping ]
- [ Sighs ]

256
00:23:36,083 --> 00:23:38,377
Another happy landing.

257
00:24:05,028 --> 00:24:08,490
[ R2-D2 Chirps ]

258
00:24:08,574 --> 00:24:12,578
- Are you coming, Master?
- Oh, no. I'm not brave enough for politics.

259
00:24:12,661 --> 00:24:14,580
I have to report to the council.

260
00:24:14,663 --> 00:24:17,124
Besides, someone needs to be the poster boy.

261
00:24:17,207 --> 00:24:21,086
Hold on.
This whole operation was your idea.

262
00:24:21,170 --> 00:24:24,298
Let us not forget, Anakin,
that you rescued me from the buzz droids.

263
00:24:24,381 --> 00:24:26,842
And you killed Count Dooku,
and you rescued the chancellor,

264
00:24:26,925 --> 00:24:28,844
carrying me unconscious on your back.

265
00:24:28,927 --> 00:24:31,471
All because of your training.

266
00:24:31,555 --> 00:24:35,100
Anakin, let's be fair. Today you were the hero,

267
00:24:35,184 --> 00:24:38,270
and you deserve your glorious day
with the politicians.

268
00:24:38,353 --> 00:24:42,441
All right. But you owe me one,
and not for saving your skin for the 10th time.

269
00:24:42,524 --> 00:24:46,778
Ninth time. That business on Cato Neimoidia
doesn't- doesn't count.

270
00:24:46,862 --> 00:24:48,780
I'll see you at the briefing.

271
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:56,663
Chancellor Palpatine, are you all right?

272
00:24:56,747 --> 00:24:59,666
Yes. Thanks to your two Jedi knights.

273
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:04,463
They killed Count Dooku,
but General Grievous has escaped once again.

274
00:25:04,546 --> 00:25:08,091
General Grievous will run and hide,
as he always does. He's a coward.

275
00:25:08,175 --> 00:25:12,513
But with Count Dooku dead,
he is the leader of the droid army.

276
00:25:12,596 --> 00:25:18,352
And I assure you, the senate will vote
to continue the war as long as Grievous is alive.

277
00:25:18,435 --> 00:25:22,523
Then the Jedi Council
will make finding Grievous our highest priority.

278
00:25:23,941 --> 00:25:25,901
Watch it.
Excuse me.

279
00:25:25,984 --> 00:25:28,987
Come along, R2.
The Republic cannot praise you enough.

280
00:25:29,071 --> 00:25:31,198
Thank you, Senator Organa.

281
00:25:31,281 --> 00:25:34,868
[ Beeping ]
Well, it couldn't possibly
be as bad as all that.

282
00:25:34,952 --> 00:25:36,912
[ Beeping ]
Now there I agree with you.

283
00:25:36,995 --> 00:25:40,374
- In fact, I could do with a tune-up myself.
- [ Beeps ]

284
00:25:40,457 --> 00:25:45,629
But the fighting will continue
until General Grievous is spare parts.

285
00:25:45,712 --> 00:25:48,215
[ Organa ]
Well, I will do everything I can in the senate.

286
00:25:48,298 --> 00:25:50,592
Excuse me.
Certainly.

287
00:25:50,676 --> 00:25:52,636
[ Chirping ]

288
00:25:58,016 --> 00:26:00,060
[ Anakin Sighs ]

289
00:26:01,186 --> 00:26:03,146
Oh, Anakin.

290
00:26:04,398 --> 00:26:07,901
- [ Sighs ]
- I've missed you, Padmé.

291
00:26:09,069 --> 00:26:12,322
There were whispers that you'd been killed.

292
00:26:12,406 --> 00:26:14,992
I'm all right.

293
00:26:15,075 --> 00:26:18,078
It feels like we've been apart for a lifetime.

294
00:26:18,161 --> 00:26:20,998
And it might have been,
if the chancellor hadn't been kidnapped.

295
00:26:21,081 --> 00:26:24,376
I don't think they would have
ever brought us back from the outer rim sieges.

296
00:26:24,459 --> 00:26:27,212
Wait. Not here.
Yes, here.

297
00:26:27,296 --> 00:26:30,799
I'm- I'm tired of all this deception.
I don't care if they know we're married.

298
00:26:30,883 --> 00:26:33,177
Anakin, don't say things like that.

299
00:26:37,848 --> 00:26:40,017
[ Sighs ]

300
00:26:41,977 --> 00:26:45,606
Are you all right? You're trembling.

301
00:26:45,689 --> 00:26:47,858
What's going on?

302
00:26:49,902 --> 00:26:52,154
Something wonderful has happened.

303
00:26:54,156 --> 00:26:57,367
Ani, I'm pregnant.

304
00:27:01,330 --> 00:27:03,248
That's-

305
00:27:03,332 --> 00:27:05,250
[ Sighs ]

306
00:27:08,378 --> 00:27:10,964
Well, that's won- That's wonderful.

307
00:27:12,674 --> 00:27:15,719
What are we gonna do?

308
00:27:17,179 --> 00:27:20,599
We're not gonna worry about anything
right now. All right?

309
00:27:20,682 --> 00:27:23,185
This is a happy moment.

310
00:27:25,145 --> 00:27:27,481
The happiest moment of my life.

311
00:28:14,945 --> 00:28:17,948
♪♪ [ Chorus Vocalizing ]

312
00:28:22,494 --> 00:28:26,707
[ Wheezing ]

313
00:28:29,668 --> 00:28:33,213
[ Coughs ]
[ Beeping ]

314
00:28:33,297 --> 00:28:36,466
Yes, Lord Sidious?

315
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:38,468
General Grievous,

316
00:28:38,552 --> 00:28:43,682
I suggest you move
the separatist leaders to Mustafar.

317
00:28:43,765 --> 00:28:47,644
It will be done, my lord.

318
00:28:47,728 --> 00:28:52,024
The end of the war is near, General.

319
00:28:52,107 --> 00:28:55,736
But the loss of Count Dooku-

320
00:28:55,819 --> 00:29:00,157
His death was a necessary loss.

321
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:04,411
Soon I will have a new apprentice-

322
00:29:04,494 --> 00:29:09,791
one far younger and more powerful.

323
00:29:36,777 --> 00:29:39,821
Ani, I want to have our baby
back home on Naboo.

324
00:29:39,905 --> 00:29:43,283
We can go to the lake country
where no one will know,

325
00:29:43,367 --> 00:29:45,285
where we can be safe.

326
00:29:46,495 --> 00:29:49,831
I can go early and fix up the baby's room.

327
00:29:51,834 --> 00:29:57,130
I know the perfect spot. Right by the gardens.

328
00:30:01,385 --> 00:30:04,721
You are so... beautiful.

329
00:30:06,306 --> 00:30:08,350
It's only because I'm so in love.

330
00:30:08,433 --> 00:30:10,894
No.
[ Chuckles ]

331
00:30:10,978 --> 00:30:14,189
No, it's because I'm so in love with you.

332
00:30:14,273 --> 00:30:17,860
So love has blinded you?
[ Chuckles ]

333
00:30:19,611 --> 00:30:21,697
Well, that's not exactly what I meant.

334
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:25,325
But it's probably true.

335
00:30:30,289 --> 00:30:32,791
[ Baby Crying ]

336
00:30:32,875 --> 00:30:36,461
[ Groans ]
Anakin, help me!

337
00:30:36,545 --> 00:30:38,463
[ Sobs ]

338
00:30:38,547 --> 00:30:41,383
[ Screaming ]

339
00:30:41,466 --> 00:30:44,720
[ Baby's Cry Fades ]
[ Panting ]

340
00:31:39,650 --> 00:31:41,610
What's bothering you?

341
00:31:43,987 --> 00:31:46,031
[ Sighs ]
Nothing.

342
00:31:47,908 --> 00:31:50,285
I remember when I gave this to you.

343
00:31:50,369 --> 00:31:54,623
How long is it gonna take
for us to be honest with each other?

344
00:31:57,167 --> 00:31:59,086
It was a dream.

345
00:31:59,169 --> 00:32:01,338
Bad?

346
00:32:01,421 --> 00:32:03,882
Like the ones I used to have
about my mother,

347
00:32:03,966 --> 00:32:05,884
just before she died.

348
00:32:05,968 --> 00:32:07,886
And?

349
00:32:10,722 --> 00:32:12,683
And it was about you.

350
00:32:15,227 --> 00:32:17,187
Tell me.

351
00:32:18,897 --> 00:32:20,858
It was only a dream.

352
00:32:33,787 --> 00:32:35,747
You die in childbirth.

353
00:32:35,831 --> 00:32:38,625
And the baby?

354
00:32:38,709 --> 00:32:41,086
I don't know.

355
00:32:42,546 --> 00:32:44,464
It was only a dream.

356
00:32:44,548 --> 00:32:47,384
I won't let this one become real.

357
00:32:48,468 --> 00:32:51,138
This baby will change our lives.

358
00:32:51,221 --> 00:32:54,141
I doubt the queen will continue to allow me
to serve in the senate.

359
00:32:54,224 --> 00:32:56,977
And if the council discovers
you're the father, you'll be expelled-

360
00:32:57,060 --> 00:32:59,605
I- I know. I know.

361
00:32:59,688 --> 00:33:03,400
Do you think Obi-Wan
might be able to help us?

362
00:33:05,402 --> 00:33:07,446
We don't need his help.

363
00:33:08,739 --> 00:33:11,783
Our baby is a blessing.

364
00:33:27,966 --> 00:33:32,137
Premonitions? Premonitions. Hmm.

365
00:33:32,221 --> 00:33:35,390
These visions you have-

366
00:33:35,474 --> 00:33:39,102
They're of pain, suffering.

367
00:33:41,021 --> 00:33:42,940
Death.

368
00:33:43,023 --> 00:33:47,444
Yourself you speak of, or someone you know?

369
00:33:48,904 --> 00:33:50,948
Someone.

370
00:33:51,031 --> 00:33:52,950
Close to you?

371
00:33:54,117 --> 00:33:56,370
Yes.

372
00:33:56,453 --> 00:34:00,332
Careful you must be
when sensing the future, Anakin.

373
00:34:00,415 --> 00:34:04,753
The fear of loss is a path to the dark side.

374
00:34:06,964 --> 00:34:10,259
I won't let these visions
come true, Master Yoda.

375
00:34:10,342 --> 00:34:13,554
Death is a natural part of life.

376
00:34:13,637 --> 00:34:18,350
Rejoice for those around you
who transform into the Force.

377
00:34:18,433 --> 00:34:21,728
Mourn them, do not. Miss them, do not.

378
00:34:21,812 --> 00:34:24,940
Attachment leads to jealousy.

379
00:34:25,023 --> 00:34:28,485
The shadow of greed that is.

380
00:34:28,569 --> 00:34:31,405
What must I do, Master Yoda?

381
00:34:31,488 --> 00:34:34,575
Train yourself to let go...

382
00:34:34,658 --> 00:34:38,120
of everything you fear to lose.

383
00:34:48,505 --> 00:34:51,258
[ Obi-Wan ] You've missed the report
on the outer rim sieges.

384
00:34:52,676 --> 00:34:55,095
I'm sorry. I was held up.

385
00:34:55,179 --> 00:34:58,765
I have no excuse.
In short, they are going very well.

386
00:34:58,849 --> 00:35:04,271
Saleucami has fallen, and Master Vos
has moved his troops to Boz Pity.

387
00:35:04,354 --> 00:35:06,398
What's wrong, then?

388
00:35:07,983 --> 00:35:09,109
The senate is expected...

389
00:35:09,193 --> 00:35:12,696
to vote more executive powers
to the chancellor today.

390
00:35:12,779 --> 00:35:17,159
Well, that can only mean less deliberating
and more action. Is that bad?

391
00:35:17,242 --> 00:35:19,703
It'll make it easier for us to end this war.

392
00:35:21,413 --> 00:35:23,749
Be careful of your friend Palpatine.

393
00:35:25,375 --> 00:35:27,294
Be careful of what?

394
00:35:27,377 --> 00:35:30,047
He has requested your presence.
What for?

395
00:35:30,130 --> 00:35:34,801
He would not say.
He didn't inform the council?

396
00:35:34,885 --> 00:35:38,347
That's unusual, isn't it?
All of this is unusual.

397
00:35:38,430 --> 00:35:40,891
And it's making me feel uneasy.

398
00:35:55,864 --> 00:35:57,783
I hope you trust me, Anakin.

399
00:35:57,866 --> 00:36:00,035
Of course.

400
00:36:01,161 --> 00:36:03,080
I need your help, son.

401
00:36:04,206 --> 00:36:06,250
What do you mean?

402
00:36:06,333 --> 00:36:11,547
I'm depending on you.
For what? I don't understand.

403
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:17,219
To be the eyes, ears
and voice of the Republic.

404
00:36:17,302 --> 00:36:19,471
Anakin,

405
00:36:19,555 --> 00:36:23,725
I'm appointing you to be my personal
representative on the Jedi Council.

406
00:36:23,809 --> 00:36:27,104
Me? A master?

407
00:36:28,689 --> 00:36:30,607
I'm overwhelmed, sir.

408
00:36:32,484 --> 00:36:35,612
But the council elects its own members.
They'll never accept this.

409
00:36:35,696 --> 00:36:39,199
I think they will. They need you.

410
00:36:39,283 --> 00:36:41,743
More than you know.

411
00:36:52,421 --> 00:36:57,217
[ Yoda ] Allow this appointment lightly
the council does not.

412
00:36:57,301 --> 00:37:00,762
Disturbing is this move
by Chancellor Palpatine.

413
00:37:01,930 --> 00:37:03,515
I understand.

414
00:37:03,599 --> 00:37:08,687
You are on this council,
but we do not grant you the rank of master.

415
00:37:08,770 --> 00:37:10,814
What?

416
00:37:15,611 --> 00:37:19,281
How can you do this? This is outrageous.

417
00:37:19,364 --> 00:37:21,533
It's unfair.

418
00:37:22,910 --> 00:37:26,163
How can you be on the council
and not be a master?

419
00:37:26,246 --> 00:37:29,791
Take a seat, young Skywalker.

420
00:37:32,836 --> 00:37:35,130
Forgive me, Master.

421
00:37:38,175 --> 00:37:41,136
[ Ki-Adi-Mundi ]
We have surveyed all systems in the Republic,

422
00:37:41,220 --> 00:37:44,973
but have found no sign of General Grievous.

423
00:37:45,057 --> 00:37:47,851
Hiding in the outer rim Grievous is.

424
00:37:47,935 --> 00:37:51,063
The outlying systems you must sweep.

425
00:37:51,146 --> 00:37:53,398
We do not have many ships to spare.

426
00:37:53,482 --> 00:37:55,692
What about the droid attack on the Wookiees?

427
00:37:55,776 --> 00:37:59,488
It is critical we send
an attack group there immediately.

428
00:37:59,571 --> 00:38:03,033
He's right. It's a system
we cannot afford to lose.

429
00:38:04,326 --> 00:38:06,453
Go I will.

430
00:38:06,537 --> 00:38:09,581
Good relations with the Wookiees I have.

431
00:38:09,665 --> 00:38:14,002
It's settled then.
Yoda will take a battalion of clones...

432
00:38:14,086 --> 00:38:16,421
to reinforce the Wookiees on Kashyyyk.

433
00:38:16,505 --> 00:38:18,590
May the Force be with us all.

434
00:38:20,801 --> 00:38:23,470
[ Anakin ]
What kind of nonsense is this?

435
00:38:23,554 --> 00:38:25,973
Put me on the council
and not make me a master?

436
00:38:26,056 --> 00:38:28,809
It's never been done
in the history of the Jedi. It's insulting.

437
00:38:28,892 --> 00:38:31,812
Oh, calm down, Anakin.
You have been given a great honor.

438
00:38:31,895 --> 00:38:35,941
To be on the council at your age-
it's never happened before.

439
00:38:36,024 --> 00:38:39,444
The fact of the matter is
you are too close to the chancellor.

440
00:38:39,528 --> 00:38:43,323
The council doesn't like it
when he interferes in Jedi affairs.

441
00:38:43,407 --> 00:38:49,162
I swear to you, I didn't ask
to be put on the council.
But it's what you wanted.

442
00:38:49,246 --> 00:38:52,583
Your friendship with Chancellor Palpatine
seems to have paid off.

443
00:38:52,666 --> 00:38:54,585
That has nothing to do with this.

444
00:38:54,668 --> 00:38:57,629
The only reason the council
has approved your appointment...

445
00:38:57,713 --> 00:39:00,716
is because the chancellor trusts you.

446
00:39:00,799 --> 00:39:03,844
And?
Anakin, I am on your side.

447
00:39:03,927 --> 00:39:07,264
I didn't want to put you
in this situation.
What situation?

448
00:39:11,310 --> 00:39:15,689
The council wants you to report
on all the chancellor's dealings.

449
00:39:15,772 --> 00:39:18,150
They want to know what he's up to.

450
00:39:22,654 --> 00:39:25,532
They want me to spy on the chancellor?

451
00:39:25,616 --> 00:39:28,285
But that's treason.
We are at war, Anakin.

452
00:39:30,287 --> 00:39:33,248
Why didn't the council give me this assignment
when we were in session?

453
00:39:33,332 --> 00:39:35,792
This assignment is not to be on record.

454
00:39:35,876 --> 00:39:39,838
The chancellor is not a bad man, Obi-Wan.

455
00:39:39,922 --> 00:39:42,966
He befriended me. He's watched out for me
ever since I arrived here.

456
00:39:43,050 --> 00:39:45,177
That is why you must help us.

457
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:48,764
Anakin, our allegiance is to the senate,
not to its leader,

458
00:39:48,847 --> 00:39:52,559
who has managed to stay in office
long after his term has expired.

459
00:39:52,643 --> 00:39:54,645
The senate demanded that he stay longer.

460
00:39:54,728 --> 00:39:57,898
Yes, but use your feelings, Anakin.
Something is out of place.

461
00:39:57,981 --> 00:40:02,569
[ Sighs ] You're asking me
to do something against the Jedi code,

462
00:40:02,653 --> 00:40:06,406
against the Republic,
against a mentor and a friend.

463
00:40:06,490 --> 00:40:10,327
That's what's out of place here.
Why are you asking this of me?

464
00:40:12,621 --> 00:40:14,540
The council is asking you.

465
00:40:21,463 --> 00:40:26,260
Anakin did not take to his new assignment
with much enthusiasm.

466
00:40:26,343 --> 00:40:29,555
[ Windu ]
It's very dangerous, putting them together.

467
00:40:29,638 --> 00:40:31,974
I don't think the boy can handle it.

468
00:40:32,057 --> 00:40:34,601
I don't trust him.

469
00:40:34,685 --> 00:40:38,564
With all due respect, Master,
is he not the chosen one?

470
00:40:38,647 --> 00:40:42,359
Is he not to destroy the Sith
and bring balance to the Force?

471
00:40:42,442 --> 00:40:45,320
So the prophecy says.

472
00:40:45,404 --> 00:40:50,325
A prophecy that misread could have been.

473
00:40:52,119 --> 00:40:54,037
He will not let me down.

474
00:40:54,121 --> 00:40:56,081
He never has.

475
00:40:56,164 --> 00:40:59,209
I hope right you are.

476
00:41:12,055 --> 00:41:13,974
[ Wookiee Grunts ]

477
00:41:22,524 --> 00:41:27,905
[ Sighs ] Sometimes I wonder
what's happening to the Jedi order.

478
00:41:27,988 --> 00:41:31,074
I think this war is destroying
the principles of the Republic.

479
00:41:32,910 --> 00:41:36,121
Have you ever considered
that we may be on the wrong side?

480
00:41:36,205 --> 00:41:38,707
What do you mean?

481
00:41:38,790 --> 00:41:43,420
What if the democracy we thought
we were serving no longer exists,

482
00:41:43,504 --> 00:41:47,132
and the Republic has become
the very evil we've been fighting to destroy?

483
00:41:47,216 --> 00:41:49,259
I don't believe that.

484
00:41:49,343 --> 00:41:51,470
And you're sounding like a separatist.

485
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:56,391
This war represents a failure to listen.

486
00:41:56,475 --> 00:41:58,519
Now you're closer
to the chancellor than anyone.

487
00:41:58,602 --> 00:42:01,897
Please, ask him to stop the fighting
and let diplomacy resume.

488
00:42:01,980 --> 00:42:04,566
Don't ask me to do that.

489
00:42:06,109 --> 00:42:09,780
Make a motion in the senate,
where that kind of a request belongs.

490
00:42:09,863 --> 00:42:12,699
- What is it?
- Nothing.

491
00:42:13,992 --> 00:42:17,871
Don't do this.
Don't shut me out. Let me help you.

492
00:42:19,915 --> 00:42:22,292
Hold me.

493
00:42:22,376 --> 00:42:25,546
Like you did by the lake on Naboo.

494
00:42:25,629 --> 00:42:29,424
So long ago,
when there was nothing but our love.

495
00:42:29,508 --> 00:42:32,970
No politics, no plotting, no war.

496
00:42:45,482 --> 00:42:49,236
♪♪ [ Droning ]

497
00:42:49,319 --> 00:42:54,491
♪♪ [ Orchestral ]

498
00:42:56,910 --> 00:42:59,830
[ Applause ]

499
00:43:04,626 --> 00:43:09,673
♪♪ [ Droning ]
[ Applause ]

500
00:43:12,176 --> 00:43:15,554
- You wanted to see me, Chancellor.
- Yes, Anakin. Come closer.

501
00:43:15,637 --> 00:43:18,265
I have good news.

502
00:43:18,348 --> 00:43:23,729
Our clone intelligence units have discovered
the location of General Grievous.

503
00:43:23,812 --> 00:43:25,731
He's hiding in the Utapau system.

504
00:43:25,814 --> 00:43:27,733
At last.

505
00:43:29,109 --> 00:43:32,321
We'll be able to capture that monster
and end this war.

506
00:43:32,404 --> 00:43:35,782
I would worry about
the collective wisdom of the council...

507
00:43:35,866 --> 00:43:38,285
if it didn't select you for this assignment.

508
00:43:38,368 --> 00:43:41,747
You're the best choice, by far.

509
00:43:43,165 --> 00:43:46,168
Hmm. Sit down.

510
00:43:46,251 --> 00:43:48,170
Leave us.

511
00:43:48,253 --> 00:43:52,299
♪♪ [ Continues ]

512
00:43:52,382 --> 00:43:55,802
[ Applause ]

513
00:44:00,140 --> 00:44:02,059
Anakin,

514
00:44:02,142 --> 00:44:06,605
you know I'm not able
to rely on the Jedi Council.

515
00:44:08,357 --> 00:44:12,569
If they haven't included you
in their plot, they soon will.

516
00:44:12,653 --> 00:44:14,780
I'm not sure I understand.

517
00:44:14,863 --> 00:44:18,575
You must sense what I have come to suspect.

518
00:44:18,659 --> 00:44:22,079
The Jedi Council want control of the Republic.

519
00:44:23,413 --> 00:44:25,958
They're planning to betray me.

520
00:44:26,041 --> 00:44:28,460
I don't think that-
Anakin.

521
00:44:29,628 --> 00:44:31,588
Search your feelings.

522
00:44:33,757 --> 00:44:36,343
You know, don't you?

523
00:44:40,722 --> 00:44:43,851
I know they don't trust you.
Hmm. Or the senate.

524
00:44:43,934 --> 00:44:48,772
Or the Republic, or democracy, for that matter.

525
00:44:48,856 --> 00:44:53,902
I have to admit,
my trust in them has been shaken.

526
00:44:53,986 --> 00:44:55,988
Why?

527
00:44:57,531 --> 00:44:59,575
They asked you to do something...

528
00:44:59,658 --> 00:45:01,952
that made you feel dishonest, didn't they?

529
00:45:04,955 --> 00:45:07,833
They asked you to spy on me, didn't they?

530
00:45:12,379 --> 00:45:14,882
I don't, uh-

531
00:45:14,965 --> 00:45:16,884
I don't know what to say.

532
00:45:16,967 --> 00:45:20,554
Remember back to your early teachings.

533
00:45:20,637 --> 00:45:24,975
All who gain power are afraid to lose it.

534
00:45:25,058 --> 00:45:29,730
Even the Jedi.
The Jedi use their power for good.

535
00:45:29,813 --> 00:45:31,982
Good is a point of view, Anakin.

536
00:45:32,065 --> 00:45:37,279
The Sith and the Jedi
are similar in almost every way,

537
00:45:39,281 --> 00:45:42,075
including their quest for greater power.

538
00:45:43,577 --> 00:45:46,622
The Sith rely on their passion
for their strength.

539
00:45:46,705 --> 00:45:49,499
They think inwards- only about themselves.

540
00:45:50,667 --> 00:45:52,920
And the Jedi don't?

541
00:45:53,003 --> 00:45:57,591
The Jedi are selfless.
They only care about others.

542
00:45:57,674 --> 00:46:00,302
[ Applause ]

543
00:46:07,768 --> 00:46:12,773
Did you ever hear the tragedy
of Darth Plagueis the Wise?

544
00:46:16,985 --> 00:46:19,446
No.
I thought not.

545
00:46:19,530 --> 00:46:21,949
It's not a story the Jedi would tell you.

546
00:46:23,367 --> 00:46:25,744
It's a Sith legend.

547
00:46:25,827 --> 00:46:27,746
Darth Plagueis...

548
00:46:27,829 --> 00:46:33,502
was a dark lord of the Sith
so powerful and so wise,

549
00:46:33,585 --> 00:46:38,465
he could use the Force
to influence the midi-chlorians...

550
00:46:38,549 --> 00:46:41,760
to create... life.

551
00:46:43,387 --> 00:46:46,473
He had such a knowledge of the dark side,

552
00:46:46,557 --> 00:46:51,603
he could even keep the ones he cared about...

553
00:46:51,687 --> 00:46:53,605
from dying.

554
00:46:57,901 --> 00:47:01,738
He could actually... save people from death?

555
00:47:01,822 --> 00:47:07,119
The dark side of the Force
is a pathway to many abilities...

556
00:47:07,202 --> 00:47:11,456
some consider to be unnatural.

557
00:47:12,541 --> 00:47:14,418
Wh- What happened to him?

558
00:47:14,501 --> 00:47:17,588
He became so powerful,

559
00:47:18,839 --> 00:47:21,842
the only thing he was afraid of was...

560
00:47:21,925 --> 00:47:23,844
losing his power.

561
00:47:23,927 --> 00:47:27,389
Which eventually, of course, he did.

562
00:47:27,472 --> 00:47:33,353
Unfortunately, he taught his apprentice
everything he knew.

563
00:47:33,437 --> 00:47:37,149
Then his apprentice killed him in his sleep.

564
00:47:39,276 --> 00:47:41,195
It's ironic.

565
00:47:41,278 --> 00:47:43,322
He could save others from death,

566
00:47:44,406 --> 00:47:46,533
but not himself.

567
00:47:50,662 --> 00:47:53,248
Is it possible to learn this power?

568
00:47:57,044 --> 00:47:59,213
Not from a Jedi.

569
00:48:16,063 --> 00:48:17,981
[ Man ]
All Red units, over here!

570
00:48:29,076 --> 00:48:32,871
[ Ki-Adi-Mundi ]
Palpatine thinks General Grievous is on Utapau?

571
00:48:32,955 --> 00:48:36,041
A partial message was intercepted
in a diplomatic packet...

572
00:48:36,124 --> 00:48:39,253
from the chairman of Utapau.
Hmm.

573
00:48:39,336 --> 00:48:42,089
Act on this we must.

574
00:48:42,172 --> 00:48:46,927
The capture of General Grievous
will end this war.

575
00:48:47,010 --> 00:48:50,889
Quickly and decisively we should proceed.

576
00:48:50,973 --> 00:48:56,019
The chancellor has requested...
that I lead the campaign.

577
00:48:56,103 --> 00:48:59,439
[ Windu ] The council will make up
its own mind who is to go,

578
00:48:59,523 --> 00:49:01,525
not the chancellor.

579
00:49:01,608 --> 00:49:06,572
A master is needed, with more experience.

580
00:49:06,655 --> 00:49:11,159
I concur. Master Kenobi should go.

581
00:49:11,243 --> 00:49:13,620
[ Yoda ]
I agree.
[ Ki-Adi-Mundi ] Aye.

582
00:49:13,704 --> 00:49:15,622
[ Windu ]
Aye.

583
00:49:15,706 --> 00:49:19,459
[ Windu ]
Very well. Council adjourned.
[ Grunts ]

584
00:49:20,502 --> 00:49:23,547
[ Wookiees Growling, Grunting ]

585
00:49:25,132 --> 00:49:28,260
[ Grunts ]
The droids have started up
their main power generators.

586
00:49:28,343 --> 00:49:33,849
Then now the time is, Commander.
Yes, sir.

587
00:49:36,101 --> 00:49:39,396
[ Roaring ]
[ All Roaring ]

588
00:49:46,028 --> 00:49:48,030
Charge!

589
00:50:02,920 --> 00:50:04,880
[ Man ]
Head for cover!

590
00:50:05,881 --> 00:50:10,761
- [ Tarzan Yell ]
- [ Roars ]

591
00:50:20,437 --> 00:50:23,357
You're gonna need me
on this one, Master.
Oh, I agree.

592
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:27,569
However, it may turn out
just to be a wild bantha chase.
Master.

593
00:50:29,613 --> 00:50:34,826
I've disappointed you. Uh, I haven't been
very appreciative of your training.

594
00:50:34,910 --> 00:50:39,331
I've been arrogant, and I apologize.

595
00:50:39,414 --> 00:50:41,792
I've just been so frustrated with the council.

596
00:50:45,087 --> 00:50:48,841
You are strong and wise, Anakin,
and I am very proud of you.

597
00:50:48,924 --> 00:50:51,552
I have trained you since you were a small boy.

598
00:50:51,635 --> 00:50:53,762
I have taught you everything I know.

599
00:50:53,846 --> 00:50:57,599
And you have become a far greater Jedi
than I could ever hope to be.

600
00:50:57,683 --> 00:51:00,394
But be patient, Anakin.

601
00:51:00,477 --> 00:51:04,481
It will not be long before the council
makes you a Jedi master.

602
00:51:11,822 --> 00:51:15,117
Obi-Wan. May the Force be with you.

603
00:51:15,200 --> 00:51:18,120
Good-bye, old friend.
May the Force be with you.

604
00:51:40,684 --> 00:51:45,272
[ Man ] Fortunately, most of the cities
are concentrated on this small continent here.

605
00:51:45,355 --> 00:51:49,443
On the far side.
I'll keep them distracted until you get there.

606
00:51:49,526 --> 00:51:52,946
Just don't take too long.
Come on. When have I
ever let you down?

607
00:51:53,030 --> 00:51:54,948
[ Chuckles ]
Very well.

608
00:51:55,032 --> 00:51:59,536
The burden is on me not to destroy
all the droids until you arrive.

609
00:52:25,145 --> 00:52:27,064
Save your energy.

610
00:52:27,147 --> 00:52:29,191
[ Sighs ]
I can't.

611
00:52:29,274 --> 00:52:31,068
Don't give up, Padmé.

612
00:52:33,278 --> 00:52:35,239
[ Sighs ]

613
00:52:44,540 --> 00:52:47,000
Obi-Wan's been here, hasn't he?

614
00:52:47,084 --> 00:52:49,169
He came by this morning.

615
00:52:50,546 --> 00:52:52,464
What did he want?

616
00:52:52,548 --> 00:52:54,508
He's worried about you.

617
00:52:56,969 --> 00:53:00,931
He says you've been
under a lot of stress.
[ Sighs ]

618
00:53:01,014 --> 00:53:03,809
I feel lost.

619
00:53:04,935 --> 00:53:08,105
Lost? What do you mean?

620
00:53:09,982 --> 00:53:12,359
Obi-Wan and the council don't trust me.

621
00:53:12,442 --> 00:53:15,904
They trust you with their lives.

622
00:53:17,614 --> 00:53:19,700
Something's happening.

623
00:53:19,783 --> 00:53:22,452
I'm not the Jedi I should be.

624
00:53:24,788 --> 00:53:26,748
I want more.

625
00:53:27,958 --> 00:53:29,877
And I know I shouldn't.

626
00:53:31,962 --> 00:53:33,964
You expect too much of yourself.

627
00:53:37,926 --> 00:53:41,138
I found a way to save you.
Save me?

628
00:53:41,221 --> 00:53:43,182
From my nightmares.

629
00:53:43,265 --> 00:53:45,225
Is that what's bothering you?

630
00:53:46,226 --> 00:53:48,896
I won't lose you, Padmé.

631
00:53:48,979 --> 00:53:51,106
I'm not gonna die in childbirth, Ani.

632
00:53:51,190 --> 00:53:53,650
I promise you.
No, I promise you.

633
00:54:14,046 --> 00:54:16,131
[ Creatures Squawking ]

634
00:54:27,559 --> 00:54:29,520
[ Squawking ]

635
00:54:37,569 --> 00:54:39,988
Greetings, young Jedi.

636
00:54:40,072 --> 00:54:43,534
What brings you to our remote sanctuary?

637
00:54:43,617 --> 00:54:45,577
Unfortunately, the war.

638
00:54:45,661 --> 00:54:50,249
There's no war here-
unless you brought it with you.

639
00:54:50,332 --> 00:54:53,544
With your kind permission,
I should like some fuel...

640
00:54:53,627 --> 00:54:59,466
and to use your city as a base
as I search nearby systems for General Grievous.

641
00:54:59,550 --> 00:55:02,845
- [ Speaking Alien Language ]
- [ Speaking Alien Language ]

642
00:55:07,558 --> 00:55:10,853
He is here. We are being held hostage.

643
00:55:10,936 --> 00:55:13,856
They are watching us.
I understand.

644
00:55:13,939 --> 00:55:18,777
Tenth level, thousands of battle droids.

645
00:55:18,861 --> 00:55:21,321
Tell your people to take shelter.

646
00:55:21,405 --> 00:55:24,408
If you have warriors, now is the time.

647
00:55:35,294 --> 00:55:39,506
Take the fighter back to the ship.
Tell Cody I've made contact.

648
00:55:39,590 --> 00:55:41,383
[ Beeping ]

649
00:55:41,466 --> 00:55:45,596
Is he bringing additional warriors?
He didn't say.

650
00:55:51,393 --> 00:55:53,312
[ Squawking ]

651
00:56:02,821 --> 00:56:05,115
[ Squawking ]

652
00:56:08,952 --> 00:56:11,246
[ Yipping ]

653
00:56:13,457 --> 00:56:15,417
[ Snarls ]

654
00:56:16,418 --> 00:56:18,879
[ Yipping ]

655
00:56:18,962 --> 00:56:21,215
[ Growls ]

656
00:56:21,298 --> 00:56:23,258
[ Yips ]

657
00:56:23,342 --> 00:56:25,344
[ Snarls ]

658
00:56:27,888 --> 00:56:33,143
It won't be long before the armies
of the Republic track us here.

659
00:56:33,227 --> 00:56:35,646
[ Wheezing ]

660
00:56:35,729 --> 00:56:40,984
I am sending you to
the Mustafar system in the outer rim.

661
00:56:46,365 --> 00:56:48,367
[ Yipping ]

662
00:56:48,450 --> 00:56:50,786
It is a volcanic planet.

663
00:56:50,869 --> 00:56:54,206
You will be safe there.
Safe?

664
00:56:54,289 --> 00:56:58,293
Hmph! Chancellor Palpatine
managed to escape your grip, General.

665
00:56:58,377 --> 00:57:02,840
Without Count Dooku, I have doubts
about your ability to keep us safe.

666
00:57:02,923 --> 00:57:05,884
[ Grievous ]
Be thankful, Viceroy,

667
00:57:05,968 --> 00:57:08,887
you have not found yourself in my grip.

668
00:57:12,349 --> 00:57:15,853
[ Grievous ]
Your ship is waiting.

669
00:57:15,936 --> 00:57:18,689
[ Coughing ]

670
00:57:20,691 --> 00:57:24,403
[ Hisses, Snorts Softly ]

671
00:57:31,952 --> 00:57:34,162
Hello there.

672
00:57:36,081 --> 00:57:41,378
General Kenobi.
[ Cackles ]

673
00:57:41,461 --> 00:57:44,006
You are a bold one.

674
00:57:44,089 --> 00:57:47,551
[ Cackles ]
Kill him.

675
00:57:56,935 --> 00:57:59,438
[ Yelping, Whining ]

676
00:58:03,358 --> 00:58:05,485
Back away.

677
00:58:05,569 --> 00:58:09,531
I will deal with this Jedi slime myself.

678
00:58:09,615 --> 00:58:11,825
Your move.

679
00:58:11,909 --> 00:58:13,827
You fool.

680
00:58:13,911 --> 00:58:19,583
I've been trained in your
Jedi arts by Count Dooku.

681
00:58:21,793 --> 00:58:24,046
[ Coughing ]

682
00:58:26,089 --> 00:58:28,592
Attack, Kenobi.

683
00:58:30,052 --> 00:58:33,222
[ Cackles ]

684
00:59:01,583 --> 00:59:02,918
[ Grievous Groans ]

685
00:59:03,001 --> 00:59:06,463
[ Growling ]

686
00:59:07,631 --> 00:59:10,467
[ Growls ]

687
00:59:15,764 --> 00:59:18,100
[ Groaning ]

688
00:59:22,104 --> 00:59:24,147
[ Grunts ]

689
00:59:26,275 --> 00:59:28,235
[ Man #1 ]
Go, go, go, go! Move it! Move it!

690
00:59:28,318 --> 00:59:30,320
Everybody out.
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

691
00:59:30,404 --> 00:59:32,322
[ Man #2 ]
Cover yourself. Come on.

692
00:59:37,452 --> 00:59:40,455
[ Cackling ]
[ Man #1 ]
Move it! Move it!

693
00:59:40,539 --> 00:59:42,040
[ Groaning ]

694
00:59:42,124 --> 00:59:43,834
[ Man #1 ]
Come on, move!
Come on, everybody!

695
00:59:44,918 --> 00:59:47,254
Army or not,

696
00:59:47,337 --> 00:59:52,467
you must realize you are doomed.

697
00:59:52,551 --> 00:59:54,553
Oh, I don't think so.
[ Grunts ]

698
01:00:13,906 --> 01:00:14,907
[ Battle Droid Screams ]

699
01:00:18,994 --> 01:00:20,495
[ Grunts ]

700
01:00:23,540 --> 01:00:26,251
- [ Whistles ]
- Uh-oh.

701
01:00:26,335 --> 01:00:28,253
[ Yipping ]

702
01:00:31,381 --> 01:00:33,383
Hyah!

703
01:00:34,801 --> 01:00:36,803
[ Screams ]

704
01:00:48,190 --> 01:00:49,900
[ Groans ]

705
01:00:52,069 --> 01:00:54,321
[ Screams ]
[ Man ]
Cover that corner.

706
01:01:00,744 --> 01:01:02,829
Master Windu, may I interrupt?

707
01:01:02,913 --> 01:01:05,707
General Kenobi has made contact
with General Grievous,

708
01:01:05,791 --> 01:01:08,085
and we have begun our attack.

709
01:01:08,168 --> 01:01:10,587
[ Windu ]
Thank you, Commander.

710
01:01:10,671 --> 01:01:13,841
Anakin, deliver this report to the chancellor.

711
01:01:13,924 --> 01:01:16,510
His reaction will give us
a clue to his intentions.

712
01:01:16,593 --> 01:01:18,762
Yes, Master.

713
01:01:25,519 --> 01:01:28,814
I sense a plot to destroy the Jedi.

714
01:01:28,897 --> 01:01:31,525
The dark side of the Force
surrounds the chancellor.

715
01:01:31,608 --> 01:01:35,988
If he does not give up his emergency powers
after the destruction of Grievous,

716
01:01:36,071 --> 01:01:38,657
then he should be removed from office.

717
01:01:38,740 --> 01:01:42,411
The Jedi Council
would have to take control of the senate...

718
01:01:42,494 --> 01:01:44,663
in order to secure a peaceful transition.

719
01:01:44,746 --> 01:01:49,209
To a dark place
this line of thought will carry us.

720
01:01:49,293 --> 01:01:54,965
Hmm. Great care we must take.

721
01:02:01,013 --> 01:02:03,182
Chancellor.

722
01:02:03,265 --> 01:02:05,809
We've just received
a report from Master Kenobi.

723
01:02:05,893 --> 01:02:08,562
He has engaged General Grievous.

724
01:02:08,645 --> 01:02:12,024
We can only hope that Master Kenobi
is up to the challenge.

725
01:02:13,859 --> 01:02:15,861
I should be there with him.

726
01:02:15,944 --> 01:02:18,322
It's upsetting to me to see that the council...

727
01:02:18,405 --> 01:02:21,700
doesn't seem to fully appreciate your talents.

728
01:02:21,783 --> 01:02:25,913
Don't you wonder
why they won't make you a Jedi master?

729
01:02:27,581 --> 01:02:29,583
I wish I knew.

730
01:02:30,876 --> 01:02:33,420
More and more I get the feeling that...

731
01:02:33,504 --> 01:02:35,756
I'm being excluded from the council.

732
01:02:42,721 --> 01:02:46,683
I know there are things about the Force
that they're not telling me.

733
01:02:48,894 --> 01:02:51,313
They don't trust you, Anakin.

734
01:02:51,396 --> 01:02:54,107
They see your future.

735
01:02:54,191 --> 01:02:59,154
They know your power
will be too strong to control.

736
01:02:59,238 --> 01:03:05,035
You must break through the fog of lies
the Jedi have created around you.

737
01:03:06,328 --> 01:03:10,457
Let me help you to know
the subtleties of the Force.

738
01:03:10,541 --> 01:03:13,335
How do you know
the ways of the Force?

739
01:03:13,418 --> 01:03:18,131
My mentor taught me everything about the Force.

740
01:03:18,215 --> 01:03:21,218
Even the nature of the dark side.

741
01:03:23,178 --> 01:03:25,514
You know the dark side?

742
01:03:25,597 --> 01:03:28,058
Anakin,

743
01:03:28,141 --> 01:03:31,478
if one is to understand the great mystery,

744
01:03:31,562 --> 01:03:34,147
one must study all its aspects,

745
01:03:34,231 --> 01:03:37,192
not just the dogmatic narrow view of the Jedi.

746
01:03:37,276 --> 01:03:41,113
If you wish to become
a complete and wise leader,

747
01:03:41,196 --> 01:03:44,867
you must embrace
a larger view of the Force.

748
01:03:44,950 --> 01:03:47,578
Be careful of the Jedi, Anakin.

749
01:03:47,661 --> 01:03:49,872
Only through me...

750
01:03:49,955 --> 01:03:53,834
can you achieve a power greater than any Jedi.

751
01:03:53,917 --> 01:03:57,254
Learn to know the dark side of the Force,

752
01:03:57,337 --> 01:04:01,008
and you will be able to save your wife...

753
01:04:01,091 --> 01:04:03,177
from certain death.

754
01:04:04,261 --> 01:04:06,180
What did you say?

755
01:04:06,263 --> 01:04:09,933
Use my knowledge. I beg you.

756
01:04:11,602 --> 01:04:13,812
You're the Sith lord.

757
01:04:13,896 --> 01:04:17,774
I know what's been troubling you.
Listen to me.

758
01:04:17,858 --> 01:04:22,446
Don't continue to be a pawn of the Jedi Council.

759
01:04:24,573 --> 01:04:28,035
Ever since I've known you,
you've been searching for a life...

760
01:04:28,118 --> 01:04:30,704
greater than that of an ordinary Jedi.

761
01:04:30,787 --> 01:04:33,207
A life of significance,

762
01:04:33,290 --> 01:04:35,667
of conscience.

763
01:04:39,796 --> 01:04:44,092
- Are you going to kill me?
- I would certainly like to.

764
01:04:45,135 --> 01:04:47,554
I know you would.

765
01:04:47,638 --> 01:04:51,475
I can feel your anger.

766
01:04:51,558 --> 01:04:54,269
It gives you focus,

767
01:04:54,353 --> 01:04:56,730
makes you stronger.

768
01:05:02,986 --> 01:05:07,115
I'm going to turn you over
to the Jedi Council.
Of course. You should.

769
01:05:07,199 --> 01:05:10,244
But you're not sure
of their intentions, are you?

770
01:05:10,327 --> 01:05:13,914
I will quickly discover the truth of all this.

771
01:05:13,997 --> 01:05:16,416
You have great wisdom, Anakin.

772
01:05:16,500 --> 01:05:20,170
Know the power of the dark side.

773
01:05:20,254 --> 01:05:23,048
Power to save Padmé.

774
01:05:25,843 --> 01:05:26,844
[ Yipping ]

775
01:05:31,974 --> 01:05:33,684
[ Yipping ]
[ Panting ]

776
01:05:50,117 --> 01:05:51,702
[ Grunts ]

777
01:05:55,038 --> 01:05:56,039
[ Yipping ]

778
01:06:19,730 --> 01:06:21,523
[ Groans ]

779
01:06:23,275 --> 01:06:25,194
[ Groans ]

780
01:06:29,072 --> 01:06:30,657
[ Growls ]

781
01:06:30,741 --> 01:06:32,451
[ Groans ]

782
01:06:32,534 --> 01:06:34,036
[ Growls ]

783
01:06:40,959 --> 01:06:42,794
[ Gasps, Shouts ]

784
01:06:43,504 --> 01:06:45,547
[ Groans ]

785
01:06:52,221 --> 01:06:54,264
Aaah!
[ Cackling ]

786
01:07:12,199 --> 01:07:14,284
[ Groans ]

787
01:07:17,496 --> 01:07:19,498
[ Groaning ]

788
01:07:26,505 --> 01:07:28,924
[ Grunts ]

789
01:07:30,801 --> 01:07:32,719
So uncivilized.

790
01:07:32,803 --> 01:07:34,805
[ Sizzling ]

791
01:07:40,227 --> 01:07:42,271
[ Anakin ]
Master Windu, I must talk to you.

792
01:07:42,354 --> 01:07:46,441
Skywalker, we just received word
that Obi-Wan has destroyed General Grievous.

793
01:07:46,525 --> 01:07:50,487
We're on our way to make sure the chancellor
returns emergency power back to the senate.

794
01:07:50,571 --> 01:07:54,324
He won't give up his power.
I've just learned a terrible truth.

795
01:07:54,408 --> 01:07:57,536
I think Chancellor Palpatine is a Sith lord.

796
01:07:57,619 --> 01:07:59,580
A Sith lord?

797
01:07:59,663 --> 01:08:02,541
Yes. The one we've been looking for.

798
01:08:02,624 --> 01:08:06,587
How do you know this?
He knows the ways of the Force.

799
01:08:06,670 --> 01:08:08,839
He's been trained to use the dark side.

800
01:08:08,922 --> 01:08:11,758
Are you sure?
Absolutely.

801
01:08:13,177 --> 01:08:15,429
Then our worst fears have been realized.

802
01:08:15,512 --> 01:08:19,016
We must move quickly
if the Jedi order is to survive.

803
01:08:19,099 --> 01:08:21,560
Master, the chancellor is very powerful.

804
01:08:21,643 --> 01:08:23,937
You'll need my help
if you're going to arrest him.

805
01:08:24,021 --> 01:08:26,982
For your own good, stay out of this affair.

806
01:08:27,065 --> 01:08:29,860
I sense a great deal of confusion in you,
young Skywalker.

807
01:08:29,943 --> 01:08:32,112
There is much fear that clouds your judgment.

808
01:08:32,196 --> 01:08:34,406
I must go, Master.
No.

809
01:08:36,366 --> 01:08:38,368
If what you've told me is true,

810
01:08:38,452 --> 01:08:40,370
you will have gained my trust.

811
01:08:40,454 --> 01:08:43,040
But for now, remain here.

812
01:08:44,208 --> 01:08:47,044
Wait in the council chambers until we return.

813
01:08:48,378 --> 01:08:50,589
[ Click, Whirring ]
Yes, Master.

814
01:09:20,327 --> 01:09:22,955
[ Palpatine's Voice ]
You do know, don't you,

815
01:09:23,038 --> 01:09:25,415
if the Jedi destroy me,

816
01:09:25,499 --> 01:09:29,503
any chance of saving her will be lost.

817
01:09:36,218 --> 01:09:39,429
♪♪ [ Vocalizing ]

818
01:09:52,276 --> 01:09:55,320
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Continues ]

819
01:10:20,888 --> 01:10:22,931
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Continues ]

820
01:10:28,979 --> 01:10:30,981
♪♪ [ Ends ]

821
01:10:58,383 --> 01:11:02,846
Master Windu. I take it General Grievous
has been destroyed then.

822
01:11:02,930 --> 01:11:06,225
I must say you're here sooner than expected.

823
01:11:06,308 --> 01:11:09,937
In the name of the Galactic Senate
of the Republic,

824
01:11:10,020 --> 01:11:11,980
you're under arrest, Chancellor.

825
01:11:12,064 --> 01:11:14,691
Are you threatening me, Master Jedi?

826
01:11:14,775 --> 01:11:16,735
The senate will decide your fate.

827
01:11:16,818 --> 01:11:20,697
- I am the senate.
- Not yet.

828
01:11:25,911 --> 01:11:28,372
It's treason then.

829
01:11:29,957 --> 01:11:31,917
[ Snarls ]

830
01:11:34,211 --> 01:11:36,213
- [ Screams ]
- [ Screams ]

831
01:11:41,218 --> 01:11:42,553
[ Screams ]

832
01:12:02,406 --> 01:12:05,242
[ Grunting ]

833
01:12:46,283 --> 01:12:48,285
[ Snarls ]

834
01:12:53,999 --> 01:12:55,959
[ Groaning ]

835
01:12:56,043 --> 01:12:58,295
[ Gasping ]

836
01:13:02,925 --> 01:13:06,011
[ Wind Howling ]

837
01:13:07,471 --> 01:13:10,891
You are under arrest, my lord.

838
01:13:11,975 --> 01:13:14,561
Anakin, I told you it would come to this.

839
01:13:14,645 --> 01:13:16,313
I was right.

840
01:13:16,396 --> 01:13:18,565
The Jedi are taking over.

841
01:13:18,649 --> 01:13:21,151
The oppression of the Sith will never return.

842
01:13:21,235 --> 01:13:23,487
You have lost.

843
01:13:23,570 --> 01:13:25,572
No.

844
01:13:25,656 --> 01:13:29,284
No. No. You will die!

845
01:13:31,328 --> 01:13:33,914
He's a traitor!

846
01:13:33,997 --> 01:13:37,334
He is the traitor!
[ Groaning ]

847
01:13:38,919 --> 01:13:43,549
I have the power to save the one you love.

848
01:13:43,632 --> 01:13:46,468
You must choose.

849
01:13:47,511 --> 01:13:50,138
Don't listen to him, Anakin!

850
01:13:51,181 --> 01:13:53,851
Don't let him kill me.

851
01:13:56,937 --> 01:13:59,690
I can't hold it any longer.

852
01:13:59,773 --> 01:14:03,026
I- I- I- I can't. I- I- I'm weak.

853
01:14:03,110 --> 01:14:05,195
I'm- I'm too weak.

854
01:14:05,279 --> 01:14:06,738
Anakin.
[ Grunts ]

855
01:14:06,822 --> 01:14:09,324
Help me. Help me!

856
01:14:10,450 --> 01:14:12,369
[ Groans ]

857
01:14:12,452 --> 01:14:15,998
I- I- I can't hold on any longer.

858
01:14:16,081 --> 01:14:19,251
I am going to end this once and for all.

859
01:14:19,334 --> 01:14:21,295
[ Anakin ]
You can't.

860
01:14:21,378 --> 01:14:23,338
He must stand trial.

861
01:14:23,422 --> 01:14:26,842
He has control of the senate and the courts.

862
01:14:26,925 --> 01:14:29,178
He's too dangerous to be left alive.

863
01:14:29,261 --> 01:14:33,265
I'm too weak. Oh. Don't kill me. Please.

864
01:14:33,348 --> 01:14:35,267
[ Anakin ]
It's not the Jedi way.

865
01:14:35,350 --> 01:14:36,894
He must live.

866
01:14:39,146 --> 01:14:41,148
Please don't.

867
01:14:41,231 --> 01:14:42,566
I need him.

868
01:14:43,567 --> 01:14:45,861
- Please don't!
- No!

869
01:14:46,778 --> 01:14:49,239
[ Screams ]

870
01:14:51,825 --> 01:14:54,620
Power!

871
01:14:56,413 --> 01:14:58,248
[ Screaming ]

872
01:15:00,334 --> 01:15:04,963
Unlimited power!

873
01:15:12,387 --> 01:15:14,389
[ Sighs ]

874
01:15:15,390 --> 01:15:18,101
What have I done?

875
01:15:18,310 --> 01:15:20,145
[ Thunder Rumbling ]

876
01:15:20,229 --> 01:15:22,439
[ Moans ]

877
01:15:26,401 --> 01:15:30,447
You're fulfilling your destiny, Anakin.

878
01:15:32,157 --> 01:15:34,284
Become my apprentice.

879
01:15:34,368 --> 01:15:39,831
Learn to use the dark side of the Force.

880
01:15:42,459 --> 01:15:45,462
I will do whatever you ask.

881
01:15:47,673 --> 01:15:50,092
Good.

882
01:15:51,760 --> 01:15:54,388
Just help me save Padmé's life.

883
01:15:56,306 --> 01:15:58,725
I can't live without her.

884
01:15:58,809 --> 01:16:01,770
[ Raspy Breathing ]

885
01:16:01,854 --> 01:16:06,775
To cheat death is a power
only one has achieved,

886
01:16:06,859 --> 01:16:10,571
but if we work together...

887
01:16:10,654 --> 01:16:14,491
I know we can discover the secret.

888
01:16:15,909 --> 01:16:18,245
I pledge myself...

889
01:16:19,621 --> 01:16:22,666
to your teachings.
[ Murmurs ]

890
01:16:22,749 --> 01:16:24,793
Good.

891
01:16:24,877 --> 01:16:27,462
Good.

892
01:16:27,546 --> 01:16:31,675
[ Raspy Breathing ]

893
01:16:33,010 --> 01:16:35,637
[ Growls Softly ]

894
01:16:35,721 --> 01:16:40,184
The Force is strong with you.

895
01:16:40,267 --> 01:16:45,856
A powerful Sith you will become.

896
01:16:45,939 --> 01:16:50,235
Henceforth you shall be known as...

897
01:16:50,319 --> 01:16:51,653
Darth...

898
01:16:53,030 --> 01:16:54,573
Vader.

899
01:16:59,161 --> 01:17:02,206
Thank you, my master.

900
01:17:04,374 --> 01:17:06,376
Rise.

901
01:17:12,716 --> 01:17:14,718
[ Murmurs ]

902
01:17:14,801 --> 01:17:17,346
[ Laser Blasts In Distance ]

903
01:17:17,429 --> 01:17:19,431
[ Sighs ]

904
01:17:19,515 --> 01:17:24,478
Because the council did not trust you,
my young apprentice,

905
01:17:26,021 --> 01:17:30,817
I believe you are the only Jedi
with no knowledge of this plot.

906
01:17:32,110 --> 01:17:34,863
When the Jedi learn what has transpired here,

907
01:17:34,947 --> 01:17:36,949
they will kill us,

908
01:17:37,032 --> 01:17:39,660
along with all the senators.

909
01:17:39,743 --> 01:17:41,745
I agree.

910
01:17:41,828 --> 01:17:45,457
The council's next move
will be against the senate.

911
01:17:45,541 --> 01:17:48,544
Every single Jedi,

912
01:17:48,627 --> 01:17:51,922
including your friend Obi-Wan Kenobi,

913
01:17:52,005 --> 01:17:55,592
is now an enemy of the Republic.

914
01:17:56,593 --> 01:17:58,595
I understand, Master.

915
01:17:58,679 --> 01:18:01,306
We must move quickly.

916
01:18:01,390 --> 01:18:03,350
The Jedi are relentless.

917
01:18:03,433 --> 01:18:09,273
If they are not all destroyed,
it will be civil war without end.

918
01:18:10,941 --> 01:18:14,945
First I want you to go to the Jedi temple.

919
01:18:15,821 --> 01:18:18,949
We will catch them off-balance.

920
01:18:19,658 --> 01:18:22,995
Do what must be done, Lord Vader.

921
01:18:23,078 --> 01:18:27,082
Do not hesitate. Show no mercy.

922
01:18:27,165 --> 01:18:31,962
Only then will you be strong enough
with the dark side...

923
01:18:32,045 --> 01:18:34,464
to save Padmé.

924
01:18:35,174 --> 01:18:39,052
What about the other Jedi
spread across the galaxy?

925
01:18:39,136 --> 01:18:42,264
Their betrayal will be dealt with.

926
01:18:44,141 --> 01:18:47,436
After you have killed
all the Jedi in the temple,

927
01:18:47,519 --> 01:18:50,230
go to the Mustafar system.

928
01:18:50,314 --> 01:18:53,609
Wipe out Viceroy Gunray...

929
01:18:53,692 --> 01:18:57,154
and the other separatist leaders.

930
01:18:57,237 --> 01:19:03,160
Once more the Sith will rule the galaxy!

931
01:19:04,369 --> 01:19:06,288
And...

932
01:19:06,371 --> 01:19:11,168
we shall have... peace.

933
01:19:54,503 --> 01:19:57,339
Sergeant, over here!

934
01:19:57,422 --> 01:19:59,508
Hurry! Follow them!

935
01:20:00,175 --> 01:20:01,385
[ Screams ]

936
01:20:01,468 --> 01:20:04,054
All Red units, let's move it!

937
01:20:04,137 --> 01:20:06,056
Come on. Let's go!

938
01:20:08,183 --> 01:20:10,018
[ Screeches ]

939
01:20:14,314 --> 01:20:16,900
[ Yipping ]

940
01:20:19,903 --> 01:20:21,947
Commander, contact your troops.

941
01:20:22,030 --> 01:20:23,991
Tell them to move to the higher levels.

942
01:20:24,074 --> 01:20:25,993
Very good, sir.

943
01:20:26,076 --> 01:20:28,245
Oh, by the way,
I think you'll be needing this.

944
01:20:28,328 --> 01:20:31,915
Thank you, Cody. Now let's get a move on.
We've got a battle to win here.

945
01:20:31,999 --> 01:20:33,917
Hyah!
Yes, sir.

946
01:20:36,587 --> 01:20:38,005
[ Beeping ]

947
01:20:40,674 --> 01:20:42,759
Commander Cody,

948
01:20:42,843 --> 01:20:46,180
the time has come.

949
01:20:46,263 --> 01:20:50,517
Execute order 66.

950
01:20:50,601 --> 01:20:52,603
Yes, my lord.

951
01:20:54,396 --> 01:20:56,982
[ Yipping ]

952
01:20:57,065 --> 01:20:58,442
Blast him!

953
01:21:01,653 --> 01:21:03,864
[ Yipping ]

954
01:21:04,990 --> 01:21:07,409
[ Screaming ]

955
01:21:25,427 --> 01:21:26,803
Come on!

956
01:21:28,889 --> 01:21:31,099
[ Weapons Cocking ]

957
01:21:33,268 --> 01:21:35,437
♪♪ [ Chorus Vocalizing ]

958
01:21:35,521 --> 01:21:37,731
[ Groans ]

959
01:21:39,274 --> 01:21:41,235
[ Squawking ]

960
01:21:41,318 --> 01:21:44,321
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Continues ]

961
01:22:00,796 --> 01:22:04,216
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Continues ]

962
01:22:12,182 --> 01:22:14,184
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Ends ]

963
01:22:16,854 --> 01:22:21,400
Execute order 66.

964
01:22:21,483 --> 01:22:23,151
It will be done, my lord.

965
01:22:45,591 --> 01:22:47,551
[ Squawking ]

966
01:23:05,944 --> 01:23:08,238
It will be done, my lord.
[ Beep ]

967
01:23:19,458 --> 01:23:22,085
[ Wookiees Roaring ]

968
01:23:24,671 --> 01:23:27,007
[ Growls ]
[ Growls ]

969
01:23:28,091 --> 01:23:31,178
[ Both Murmuring, Roaring ]

970
01:23:44,775 --> 01:23:47,194
Master Skywalker, there are too many of them.

971
01:23:47,277 --> 01:23:49,279
What are we going to do?

972
01:23:59,748 --> 01:24:03,919
The chancellor's office indicated
Master Anakin returned to the Jedi temple.

973
01:24:04,002 --> 01:24:07,130
Don't worry. I- I'm sure he'll be all right.

974
01:24:17,933 --> 01:24:19,476
♪♪ [ Chorus Vocalizing ]

975
01:24:36,326 --> 01:24:39,413
- What's going on here?
- There's been a rebellion, sir.

976
01:24:39,496 --> 01:24:42,082
Don't worry. The situation is under control.

977
01:24:42,165 --> 01:24:45,460
I'm sorry, sir. It's time for you to leave.

978
01:24:47,171 --> 01:24:49,131
And so it is.

979
01:24:49,214 --> 01:24:51,216
♪♪ [ Vocalizing Ends ]

980
01:24:52,759 --> 01:24:55,470
- [ Lightsaber Activates ]
- Get him!

981
01:25:06,106 --> 01:25:08,025
No!

982
01:25:11,612 --> 01:25:14,198
Don't worry about him.
Let him go.

983
01:25:24,249 --> 01:25:26,668
[ Grunting ]

984
01:25:30,464 --> 01:25:32,424
[ Beeping ]

985
01:25:41,058 --> 01:25:44,019
All these Wookiees are dead.
Move to the east.

986
01:25:44,102 --> 01:25:46,104
Yes, sir.

987
01:25:50,234 --> 01:25:52,236
[ Murmurs ]

988
01:25:53,695 --> 01:25:55,614
Good-bye, Tarfful.

989
01:25:55,697 --> 01:25:57,658
Good-bye, Chewbacca.

990
01:25:57,741 --> 01:25:59,409
[ Roars ]

991
01:25:59,493 --> 01:26:02,412
Miss you I will.

992
01:26:02,496 --> 01:26:04,414
[ Roars Softly ]

993
01:26:06,291 --> 01:26:08,293
[ Both Murmuring ]

994
01:26:08,377 --> 01:26:09,545
[ Roars ]

995
01:26:16,301 --> 01:26:18,262
[ Both Murmuring ]

996
01:26:24,977 --> 01:26:27,229
[ Murmurs ]

997
01:26:27,312 --> 01:26:29,606
[ Roars ]

998
01:26:39,408 --> 01:26:41,702
Hopefully we'll be able to intercept a few Jedi...

999
01:26:41,785 --> 01:26:44,204
before they walk into this catastrophe.

1000
01:26:49,835 --> 01:26:51,795
[ Cody ]
Did you find Kenobi?

1001
01:26:51,879 --> 01:26:53,881
Sir, no one could have survived that fall.

1002
01:26:53,964 --> 01:26:57,301
[ Cody ]
Start loading your men on the ships.

1003
01:26:57,384 --> 01:27:00,179
Move it.

1004
01:27:29,958 --> 01:27:32,085
[ Beeping ]

1005
01:27:32,169 --> 01:27:34,213
Emergency code 913.

1006
01:27:34,296 --> 01:27:36,215
I have no contact on any frequency.

1007
01:27:38,258 --> 01:27:40,385
[ Distorted ]
Master Kenobi.

1008
01:27:40,469 --> 01:27:42,471
Repeat.
Master Kenobi.

1009
01:27:42,554 --> 01:27:46,475
Senator Organa.
My clone troops turned on me. I need help.

1010
01:27:46,558 --> 01:27:49,186
We have just rescued Master Yoda.

1011
01:27:49,269 --> 01:27:51,605
It appears this ambush has happened everywhere.

1012
01:27:51,688 --> 01:27:53,857
We're sending you our coordinates.

1013
01:28:00,531 --> 01:28:03,492
[ Beeping ]
Hush! Not so loud.

1014
01:28:03,575 --> 01:28:06,620
Are you all right?
I heard there was an attack on the Jedi temple.

1015
01:28:06,703 --> 01:28:09,206
You could see the smoke from here.
I'm fine. I'm fine.

1016
01:28:09,289 --> 01:28:12,835
I came to see if you
and the baby are safe.
What's happening?

1017
01:28:12,918 --> 01:28:15,796
The Jedi have tried to overthrow the Republic.

1018
01:28:15,879 --> 01:28:18,465
I can't believe that.

1019
01:28:18,549 --> 01:28:23,136
I saw Master Windu attempt
to assassinate the chancellor myself.

1020
01:28:23,220 --> 01:28:26,723
Oh, Anakin. What are you gonna do?

1021
01:28:35,399 --> 01:28:37,609
I will not betray the Republic.

1022
01:28:39,570 --> 01:28:41,572
My loyalties lie with the chancellor...

1023
01:28:42,656 --> 01:28:45,409
and with the senate and with you.

1024
01:28:45,492 --> 01:28:47,703
What about Obi-Wan?

1025
01:28:47,786 --> 01:28:50,038
I don't know.

1026
01:28:50,122 --> 01:28:52,249
Many Jedi have been killed.

1027
01:28:52,332 --> 01:28:56,170
We can only hope that he's remained
loyal to the chancellor.

1028
01:28:56,253 --> 01:28:58,630
Anakin, I'm afraid.

1029
01:29:00,549 --> 01:29:03,677
Have faith, my love.

1030
01:29:03,760 --> 01:29:06,096
Everything will soon be set right.

1031
01:29:06,180 --> 01:29:09,600
The chancellor has given me
a very important mission.

1032
01:29:09,683 --> 01:29:12,895
The separatists have gathered
on the Mustafar system.

1033
01:29:12,978 --> 01:29:15,522
I'm going there to end this war.

1034
01:29:15,606 --> 01:29:17,524
Wait for me until I return.

1035
01:29:17,608 --> 01:29:20,027
Things will be different. I promise.

1036
01:29:25,824 --> 01:29:27,826
Please, wait for me.

1037
01:29:29,369 --> 01:29:31,788
[ R2-D2 Beeps ]

1038
01:29:31,872 --> 01:29:34,625
Well, he is under a lot of stress, R2.

1039
01:29:34,708 --> 01:29:36,752
[ Beeping, Whistling ]

1040
01:29:36,835 --> 01:29:38,795
Take care, my little friend.

1041
01:29:43,050 --> 01:29:46,762
Oh, my lady, is there anything I might do?

1042
01:29:46,845 --> 01:29:49,389
No, thank you, 3PO.

1043
01:29:49,473 --> 01:29:54,228
Oh. I- I feel so helpless.

1044
01:30:17,042 --> 01:30:20,420
How many other Jedi
have managed to survive?

1045
01:30:20,504 --> 01:30:23,841
Heard from no one have we.

1046
01:30:23,924 --> 01:30:27,052
I saw thousands of troops
attack the Jedi temple.

1047
01:30:27,135 --> 01:30:29,054
That's why I went looking for Yoda.

1048
01:30:29,137 --> 01:30:31,723
Have we had any contact
from the temple?

1049
01:30:31,807 --> 01:30:34,685
Received a coded retreat message we have.

1050
01:30:34,768 --> 01:30:38,814
It requests all Jedi to return to the temple.

1051
01:30:38,897 --> 01:30:42,359
It says the war is over.
Well, then we must go back.

1052
01:30:42,442 --> 01:30:45,946
If there are any stragglers,
they will fall into the trap and be killed.

1053
01:30:46,029 --> 01:30:50,909
Hmm. Suggest dismantling
the coded signal, do you?

1054
01:30:50,993 --> 01:30:53,745
Yes, Master. There is too much at stake.

1055
01:30:53,829 --> 01:30:56,415
I agree.

1056
01:30:56,498 --> 01:31:00,127
And a little more knowledge might light our way.

1057
01:31:21,064 --> 01:31:24,526
The plan has gone
as you had promised, my lord.

1058
01:31:24,610 --> 01:31:27,404
You have done well, Viceroy.

1059
01:31:27,487 --> 01:31:33,327
When my new apprentice Darth Vader arrives,

1060
01:31:33,410 --> 01:31:36,955
he will take care of you.

1061
01:31:48,550 --> 01:31:51,678
We're receiving a message
from the chancellor's office, sir.

1062
01:31:51,762 --> 01:31:53,764
Send it through.
Yes, sir.

1063
01:31:55,474 --> 01:32:00,187
Senator Organa, the supreme chancellor
requests your presence...

1064
01:32:00,270 --> 01:32:02,272
at a special session of Congress.

1065
01:32:02,356 --> 01:32:05,943
- I will be there.
- He'll be expecting you.

1066
01:32:08,904 --> 01:32:12,199
- Could be a trap.
- I don't think so.

1067
01:32:12,282 --> 01:32:15,410
The chancellor will not be able to control
the thousands of star systems...

1068
01:32:15,494 --> 01:32:17,454
without keeping the senate intact.

1069
01:32:18,372 --> 01:32:21,583
If a special session of Congress there is,

1070
01:32:21,667 --> 01:32:25,337
easier for us to enter
the Jedi temple it will be.

1071
01:32:48,402 --> 01:32:51,071
[ Whistles ]

1072
01:33:00,956 --> 01:33:03,375
[ Whistles ]

1073
01:33:03,458 --> 01:33:05,460
R2, stay with the ship.

1074
01:33:07,713 --> 01:33:09,882
[ Beeping, Whistling ]

1075
01:33:14,011 --> 01:33:17,264
[ Speaking Geonosian ]

1076
01:33:17,347 --> 01:33:21,018
[ Beeping, Squeaking ]

1077
01:33:30,152 --> 01:33:33,906
Welcome, Lord Vader. We've been expecting you.

1078
01:33:46,293 --> 01:33:48,295
[ Screams ]

1079
01:33:50,047 --> 01:33:52,090
[ Shouts ]

1080
01:33:52,174 --> 01:33:54,551
[ Groans ]
[ Thud ]

1081
01:33:55,594 --> 01:33:57,596
[ Groans ]

1082
01:33:57,679 --> 01:33:59,890
[ Grunts ]

1083
01:34:03,727 --> 01:34:05,646
[ Applause ]

1084
01:34:05,729 --> 01:34:10,275
[ Palpatine ]
And the Jedi rebellion has been foiled.

1085
01:34:10,359 --> 01:34:12,653
What's happened?
The chancellor's been elaborating...

1086
01:34:12,736 --> 01:34:16,073
on a plot by the Jedi
to overthrow the senate.

1087
01:34:16,156 --> 01:34:21,662
The remaining Jedi
will be hunted down and defeated.

1088
01:34:21,745 --> 01:34:23,747
[ Applause ]

1089
01:34:37,427 --> 01:34:39,930
Not even the younglings survived.

1090
01:34:41,014 --> 01:34:42,975
Killed not by clones...

1091
01:34:43,058 --> 01:34:46,311
this Padawan.

1092
01:34:47,396 --> 01:34:50,065
By a lightsaber he was.

1093
01:34:56,905 --> 01:35:00,492
Who? Who could have done this?

1094
01:35:03,245 --> 01:35:05,247
[ Groans ]

1095
01:35:08,166 --> 01:35:11,086
[ Applause ]

1096
01:35:11,170 --> 01:35:14,381
The attempt on my life...

1097
01:35:14,464 --> 01:35:17,134
has left me scarred...

1098
01:35:17,217 --> 01:35:20,220
and deformed.

1099
01:35:20,304 --> 01:35:23,223
But I assure you.

1100
01:35:23,307 --> 01:35:28,061
My resolve has never been stronger!

1101
01:35:28,145 --> 01:35:31,023
[ Applause ]

1102
01:35:32,232 --> 01:35:36,111
Stop! No!
[ Screams ]

1103
01:35:36,195 --> 01:35:38,363
[ Groans ]

1104
01:35:39,573 --> 01:35:42,492
♪♪ [ Chorus Vocalizing ]

1105
01:35:45,746 --> 01:35:49,416
In order to ensure the security...

1106
01:35:49,499 --> 01:35:52,085
and continuing stability,

1107
01:35:52,169 --> 01:35:56,089
the Republic will be reorganized...

1108
01:35:56,173 --> 01:36:01,637
into the first Galactic Empire!

1109
01:36:01,720 --> 01:36:03,764
[ Applause ]
For a safe...

1110
01:36:03,847 --> 01:36:08,435
and secure society.

1111
01:36:08,519 --> 01:36:11,647
[ Applause ]
♪♪ [ Chorus Vocalizing ]

1112
01:36:17,819 --> 01:36:20,531
So this is how liberty dies.

1113
01:36:20,614 --> 01:36:23,367
With thunderous applause.

1114
01:36:25,744 --> 01:36:27,955
The war is over.

1115
01:36:28,038 --> 01:36:32,167
Lord Sidious promised us peace.
We only want-

1116
01:36:32,251 --> 01:36:33,710
[ Screams ]

1117
01:36:34,920 --> 01:36:36,922
♪♪ [ Ends ]

1118
01:36:40,300 --> 01:36:45,013
I have recalibrated the code,
warning all surviving Jedi to stay away.

1119
01:36:45,097 --> 01:36:47,558
For the clones...

1120
01:36:47,641 --> 01:36:51,770
to discover the recalibration
a long time it will take.

1121
01:37:04,074 --> 01:37:06,159
Wait. Master.

1122
01:37:06,243 --> 01:37:09,454
There is something I must know.

1123
01:37:15,544 --> 01:37:18,005
If into the security recordings you go,

1124
01:37:18,088 --> 01:37:20,007
only pain will you find.

1125
01:37:20,090 --> 01:37:23,594
I must know the truth, Master.

1126
01:37:26,430 --> 01:37:29,391
[ Murmurs Softly ]

1127
01:37:30,434 --> 01:37:32,394
It can't be.

1128
01:37:32,477 --> 01:37:34,396
It can't be.

1129
01:37:34,479 --> 01:37:38,567
You have done well, my new apprentice.

1130
01:37:38,650 --> 01:37:41,695
Now, Lord Vader,

1131
01:37:41,778 --> 01:37:45,324
go and bring peace to the Empire.

1132
01:37:45,407 --> 01:37:47,576
I can't watch any more.

1133
01:37:47,659 --> 01:37:52,289
Destroy the Sith we must.

1134
01:37:54,041 --> 01:37:56,168
Send me to kill the emperor.

1135
01:37:56,251 --> 01:37:58,545
I will not kill Anakin.

1136
01:37:58,629 --> 01:38:03,383
To fight this Lord Sidious,
strong enough you are not.

1137
01:38:03,467 --> 01:38:06,720
He is like my brother. I cannot do it.

1138
01:38:06,803 --> 01:38:12,559
Twisted by the dark side
young Skywalker has become.

1139
01:38:12,643 --> 01:38:16,063
The boy you trained, gone he is.

1140
01:38:16,146 --> 01:38:19,066
Consumed by Darth Vader.

1141
01:38:19,149 --> 01:38:22,194
I do not know where the emperor has sent him.

1142
01:38:22,277 --> 01:38:24,530
I don't know where to look.

1143
01:38:25,822 --> 01:38:29,535
Use your feelings, Obi-Wan,
and find him you will.

1144
01:38:40,045 --> 01:38:42,673
When was the last time you saw him?

1145
01:38:42,756 --> 01:38:46,176
Yesterday.
And do you know where he is now?

1146
01:38:47,219 --> 01:38:49,221
No.

1147
01:38:49,304 --> 01:38:52,933
Padmé, I need your help.

1148
01:38:53,016 --> 01:38:56,019
He is in grave danger.
From the Sith?

1149
01:38:56,103 --> 01:38:58,105
From himself.

1150
01:39:00,524 --> 01:39:02,609
Padmé,

1151
01:39:02,693 --> 01:39:05,112
Anakin has turned to the dark side.

1152
01:39:05,195 --> 01:39:08,699
You're wrong. How could you even say that?

1153
01:39:11,451 --> 01:39:15,289
I have seen a- a security hologram...

1154
01:39:15,372 --> 01:39:17,833
of him...

1155
01:39:17,916 --> 01:39:19,835
killing younglings.

1156
01:39:19,918 --> 01:39:22,963
Not Anakin. He couldn't.

1157
01:39:23,046 --> 01:39:26,049
He was deceived by a lie. We all were.

1158
01:39:26,133 --> 01:39:30,679
It appears that the chancellor
is behind everything, including the war.

1159
01:39:32,472 --> 01:39:35,225
Palpatine is the Sith lord
we've been looking for.

1160
01:39:35,309 --> 01:39:39,438
After the death of Count Dooku,
Anakin became his new apprentice.

1161
01:39:45,611 --> 01:39:47,613
I don't believe you.

1162
01:39:48,989 --> 01:39:50,991
I can't.

1163
01:39:56,079 --> 01:39:57,247
Padmé,

1164
01:39:58,665 --> 01:40:00,959
I must find him.

1165
01:40:03,420 --> 01:40:05,422
You're going to kill him, aren't you?

1166
01:40:09,092 --> 01:40:11,595
He has become a very great threat.

1167
01:40:14,181 --> 01:40:16,183
I can't.

1168
01:40:29,363 --> 01:40:31,323
Anakin is the father, isn't he?

1169
01:40:35,786 --> 01:40:37,287
I'm so sorry.

1170
01:41:23,500 --> 01:41:25,002
[ Typho ]
Milady, let me come with you.

1171
01:41:25,085 --> 01:41:28,046
[ Padmé ] There's no danger.
The fighting's over. And this is personal.

1172
01:41:28,130 --> 01:41:30,549
As you wish, milady, but I strongly disagree.

1173
01:41:30,632 --> 01:41:34,303
I'll be all right, Captain.
This is something I must do myself.

1174
01:41:34,386 --> 01:41:36,805
Besides, 3PO will look after me.

1175
01:41:38,640 --> 01:41:40,642
[ C-3PO ]
Oh, dear.

1176
01:41:51,236 --> 01:41:53,363
- [ Beep ]
- Do you know?

1177
01:41:53,447 --> 01:41:57,075
I think I'm beginning to get the hang
of this flying business. Hmm.

1178
01:41:57,159 --> 01:42:01,038
[ Revving ]

1179
01:42:24,436 --> 01:42:27,898
The separatists
have been taken care of, my master.

1180
01:42:27,981 --> 01:42:30,901
It is finished then.

1181
01:42:32,277 --> 01:42:38,116
You have restored
peace and justice to the galaxy.

1182
01:42:38,200 --> 01:42:43,121
Send a message to the ships
of the Trade Federation.

1183
01:42:43,205 --> 01:42:48,377
All droid units
must shut down immediately.

1184
01:42:48,460 --> 01:42:50,587
Very good, my lord.

1185
01:42:51,713 --> 01:42:53,715
[ Beeping ]

1186
01:43:38,010 --> 01:43:40,304
[ Hatch Opens ]

1187
01:43:50,480 --> 01:43:52,608
[ Anakin ]
I saw your ship.

1188
01:43:55,402 --> 01:43:58,447
What are you doing out here?
I was so worried about you.

1189
01:43:59,865 --> 01:44:02,743
Obi-Wan told me terrible things.

1190
01:44:02,826 --> 01:44:04,995
What things?

1191
01:44:05,078 --> 01:44:08,040
He said you've turned to the dark side.

1192
01:44:08,123 --> 01:44:10,542
That you...

1193
01:44:10,626 --> 01:44:12,794
killed younglings.

1194
01:44:14,296 --> 01:44:17,007
Obi-Wan is trying to turn you against me.

1195
01:44:17,090 --> 01:44:20,886
He cares about us.
Us?

1196
01:44:20,969 --> 01:44:23,722
He knows.

1197
01:44:23,805 --> 01:44:25,724
He wants to help you.

1198
01:44:29,686 --> 01:44:32,814
Anakin, all I want is your love.

1199
01:44:32,898 --> 01:44:35,275
Love won't save you, Padmé.

1200
01:44:35,359 --> 01:44:38,612
Only my new powers can do that.
At what cost?

1201
01:44:38,695 --> 01:44:41,114
You're a good person. Don't do this.

1202
01:44:41,198 --> 01:44:43,951
I won't lose you the way I lost my mother.

1203
01:44:44,034 --> 01:44:48,288
I am becoming more powerful
than any Jedi has ever dreamed of.

1204
01:44:48,372 --> 01:44:51,208
And I'm doing it for you. To protect you.

1205
01:44:53,001 --> 01:44:54,461
Come away with me.

1206
01:44:54,545 --> 01:44:57,256
Help me raise our child.

1207
01:44:57,339 --> 01:45:01,593
Leave everything else behind
while we still can.
Don't you see?

1208
01:45:01,677 --> 01:45:04,930
We don't have to run away anymore.

1209
01:45:05,013 --> 01:45:07,558
I have brought peace to the Republic.

1210
01:45:07,641 --> 01:45:10,519
I am more powerful than the chancellor.

1211
01:45:10,602 --> 01:45:12,729
I- I can overthrow him.

1212
01:45:14,773 --> 01:45:17,860
And together, you and I can rule the galaxy,

1213
01:45:17,943 --> 01:45:20,404
make things the way we want them to be.

1214
01:45:26,702 --> 01:45:28,745
I don't believe what I'm hearing.

1215
01:45:30,205 --> 01:45:33,542
Obi-Wan was right. You've changed.

1216
01:45:35,711 --> 01:45:38,589
I don't want to hear any more about Obi-Wan.

1217
01:45:38,672 --> 01:45:42,885
The Jedi turned against me.
Don't you turn against me.

1218
01:45:44,553 --> 01:45:46,597
I don't know you anymore.

1219
01:45:48,182 --> 01:45:50,184
Anakin,

1220
01:45:50,267 --> 01:45:52,853
you're breaking my heart.

1221
01:45:52,936 --> 01:45:55,939
You're going down a path I can't follow.

1222
01:45:56,023 --> 01:45:58,817
Because of Obi-Wan?

1223
01:45:58,901 --> 01:46:01,695
Because of what you've done.

1224
01:46:01,778 --> 01:46:03,739
What you plan to do.

1225
01:46:04,948 --> 01:46:07,618
Stop. Stop now. Come back.

1226
01:46:07,701 --> 01:46:10,662
I love you.
Liar!

1227
01:46:10,746 --> 01:46:11,663
[ Gasps ]

1228
01:46:13,498 --> 01:46:15,375
No.

1229
01:46:15,459 --> 01:46:19,213
You're with him!
You brought him here to kill me.

1230
01:46:19,296 --> 01:46:22,299
- No.
- Let her go, Anakin.

1231
01:46:23,800 --> 01:46:25,385
Anakin.

1232
01:46:25,469 --> 01:46:27,679
Let her go.

1233
01:46:29,431 --> 01:46:31,308
[ Gasps ]

1234
01:46:37,648 --> 01:46:39,691
You turned her against me!

1235
01:46:41,276 --> 01:46:43,487
You have done that yourself.

1236
01:46:48,200 --> 01:46:50,410
You will not take her from me!

1237
01:46:50,494 --> 01:46:54,373
Your anger and your lust for power
have already done that.

1238
01:46:57,501 --> 01:47:02,673
You have allowed this dark lord
to twist your mind, until now-

1239
01:47:04,216 --> 01:47:07,427
until now you have become
the very thing you swore to destroy.

1240
01:47:07,511 --> 01:47:09,429
Don't lecture me, Obi-Wan.

1241
01:47:09,513 --> 01:47:12,057
I see through the lies of the Jedi.

1242
01:47:13,141 --> 01:47:15,561
I do not fear the dark side as you do.

1243
01:47:17,354 --> 01:47:19,314
I have brought peace,

1244
01:47:19,398 --> 01:47:21,108
freedom, justice...

1245
01:47:21,191 --> 01:47:25,070
and security to my new empire.

1246
01:47:25,153 --> 01:47:28,031
Your new empire?

1247
01:47:28,115 --> 01:47:31,451
Don't make me kill you.

1248
01:47:31,535 --> 01:47:36,081
Anakin, my allegiance
is to the Republic, to democracy!

1249
01:47:36,164 --> 01:47:38,792
If you're not with me,

1250
01:47:39,793 --> 01:47:41,712
then you're my enemy.

1251
01:47:43,714 --> 01:47:46,216
Only a Sith deals in absolutes.

1252
01:47:48,802 --> 01:47:50,262
I will do what I must.

1253
01:47:51,305 --> 01:47:53,724
You will try.

1254
01:47:55,184 --> 01:47:57,269
[ Shouts ]

1255
01:47:57,352 --> 01:47:59,730
[ Both Grunting ]

1256
01:48:14,912 --> 01:48:16,079
[ Grunts ]

1257
01:48:25,464 --> 01:48:29,510
I hear a new apprentice you have, Emperor.

1258
01:48:29,593 --> 01:48:34,097
Or should I call you Darth Sidious?

1259
01:48:34,181 --> 01:48:36,433
Master Yoda.

1260
01:48:36,517 --> 01:48:38,602
You survived.

1261
01:48:38,685 --> 01:48:41,438
Surprised?

1262
01:48:41,522 --> 01:48:46,151
Your arrogance blinds you, Master Yoda.

1263
01:48:46,235 --> 01:48:48,320
Now you will experience...

1264
01:48:48,403 --> 01:48:52,908
the full power of the dark side.

1265
01:49:30,654 --> 01:49:33,657
[ Cackling ]

1266
01:49:34,825 --> 01:49:38,537
I have waited a long time...

1267
01:49:38,620 --> 01:49:41,206
for this moment,

1268
01:49:41,290 --> 01:49:45,836
my little green friend.

1269
01:49:47,337 --> 01:49:50,883
[ Cackling ]

1270
01:49:51,884 --> 01:49:54,761
[ Cackling Continues ]

1271
